\id NEH
\h Naḥamya 
\toc1 Naḥamya 
\toc2 Naḥamya 
\toc3 Naḥ. 
\mt1 Naḥamya  
\c 1
\s1 Tazaǧit n Naḥamya i řgens n Israil  
\m
\v 1 \bd Awařen n Naḥamya, mmis n Ḥakalya.\bd*  
\m Imsar deg uyur n Kisluw, deg useggʷas wiss ɛicrin, umi d ayi tuɣa di řeqṣar di Cucan,  
\v 2 aqa yusa-dd Ḥanani, ijjen zeg aytma, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d ca n yeryazen zi Yahuda, uca sseqsiɣ ten x Wudayen nni innejmen, inni iqqimen zi tmeḥbast, u x Urcalim.  
\v 3 Nitni nnan ayi: “Inni iqqimen, inni din iqqimen di lɛamala zi tmeḥbast, aqa aten di řeɣben d ameqqran u di řefḍiḥet u řḥiḍ n Urcalim ittwarẓ u tiwwura nnes ttwasscemḍent.”   
\m
\v 4 Umi sřiɣ awařen-a, imsar, aqa qqimeɣ \add ɣar temmurt\add*, ruɣ u ceḍneɣ ca n wussan, ẓummeɣ u ẓuǧeɣ zzat i wudem n AREBBI n ijenwan.  
\v 5 Nniɣ: “A SIDI, AREBBI n ijenwan, Cek d Arebbi d ameqqran issaggʷaden, wenni iṭṭfen di Řɛahd d tmexsiwt icewwaren di ṭṭweɛ n yinni Cek ittexsen u n yinni iṭṭfen di tweṣṣa nnec, \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt  Uf. 20:6; 34:7; Řxř. 14:18; Aɛwd. 5:10; Izhd. 86:15; 103:8; 145:8; Dan. 9:4 \x*  
\v 6 ejj ad yiři umezzuɣ nnec iften u tiṭṭawin nnec arzment, ḥima ad tesřed i tẓaǧit n umsexxar nnec nni ẓuǧeɣ ass-a zzat i wudem nnec, ass d ǧiřet, di ṭṭweɛ n ayt n Israil, imsexxaren nnec. Neɛmeɣ \add ɛawed\add* s ddnub n ayt n Israil i zi xak xḍan. Necc d taddart n baba, aqa nexḍa \add akidek\add*.  
\v 7 Negga akidek s waṭṭas n řeɣdar u war neṭṭif ca di řumurat d tweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ i zi tumured i umsexxar nnec Musa.  
\v 8 Idar awař i tumured i umsexxar nnec Musa umi tennid: “Mařa kenniw d iɣeddaren, aqa ad kenniw sszeǧɛeɣ jar řegnus, \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Aɛwd. 4:25, 26, 27; 30:2, 3, 4\x*  
\v 9 \add maca mařa\add* tdewřem-dd ɣari, ad ṭṭfem di řumurat inu u ad tent teggem, waxxa din zzaywem inni x yuẓẓřen ɣar ṭṭarf aneggar n ujenna, Necc ad ten ssmuneɣ ssenni, ad ten awyeɣ ɣar wemcan i ixḍareɣ Necc ḥima ad dinni ssezdɣeɣ Isem inu.  
\v 10 Nitni \add wah,\add* d imsexxaren nnec d řgens nnec nni tfekked s jjehd nnec ameqqran u s ufus nnec ijehden.  
\v 11 A, Sidi inu, ejj ad iften umezzuɣ nnec ɣar tẓaǧit n umsexxar nnec u ɣar tẓaǧit n imsexxaren nni ittexsen ad tteggʷeden zeg Yisem nnec. Ejj amsexxar nnec ad yaweḍ ass-a u ewc as arreḥmet zzat i wudem n weryaz-a.” Necc tuɣa ayi d awarrad n ujeǧid.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Ajeǧid Artaḥcasta n Lfurs issekk Naḥamya i Urcalim  
\m
\v 1 Deg uyur n Nisan, deg useggʷas wiss ɛicrin n ujeǧid Artaḥcasta, \add umi\add* tuɣa din binu zzat i wudem nnes, imsar, aqa ksiɣ binu uca wciɣ t i ujeǧid. Ɛemmarṣ war nzemmeɣ zzat i wudem nnes.  
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi ujeǧid: “Mayemmi inzemm wudem nnec, u cek war teḥřiced ca? Aqa man aya war iǧi mɣir d ijj n řḥař n wuř ibarrcnen.” \add Xenni\add* dewřeɣ nnxeřɛeɣ aṭṭas.  
\v 3 Nniɣ i ujeǧid: “Tudart i ujeǧid i řebda. Mammec war ittiři wudem inu inzemm, aqa tandint, amcan n imeḍřan n řejdud inu, d řxarbet d tewwura nnes tecca i-tent tmessi?”  
\v 4 Inna ayi ujeǧid: “Man \add xenni\add* min tᵉttared cek?” \add Xenni\add* ẓuǧeɣ i AREBBI n ijenwan  
\v 5 uca nniɣ i ujeǧid: “Mařa tusa as-dd i ujeǧid x řxaḍar u yufa amsexxar nnec arḍa zzat i wudem nnec, sekk ayi-dd xenni ɣar Yahuda, ɣar tendint n imeḍřan n řejdud inu, ḥima ad tt bniɣ ɛawed.”  
\v 6 \add Xas uca\add* inna ayi ujeǧid, umi teqqim tjeǧidt x uɣezdis nnes: “Mecḥař i ɣa tekk twaḥit nnec u meřmi i dd ɣa tɛeqbed?” Umi d as nniɣ \add řqedd n\add* ijj n řmijař, ittɣiř as man aya mliḥ i ujeǧid, uca issekk ayi \add dinni\add*.   
\m
\v 7 Arniɣ nniɣ as i ujeǧid: “Mařa tusa as-dd i ujeǧid x řxaḍar, \add xenni\add* ad ayi mmewcent tebratin i lwulat \add n temmurt\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, maḥend ad ayi yarzmen tawwart maḥend ad awḍeɣ ɣar Yahuda,  
\v 8 uřa d ict n tebrat i Asaf, aɛessas n weftis n ujeǧid nni iǧan am jjennet, ḥima ad ayi yewc akeccuḍ ḥima ad \add zzayes\add* negg tiḥenya i tzeqqa sennej i tewwura n řeqṣar nni \add iǧan\add* zzat i Taddart, u i řḥiḍ n tendint, u i taddart mani ɣa zedɣeɣ.” Uca iwca ayi tent ujeǧid minzi afus aṣebḥan n AREBBI tuɣa t xafi.  
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* iwḍeɣ ɣar lwulat \add di temmurt\add* x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add* u wciɣ asen tibratin n ujeǧid. Ajeǧid issekk akidi uřa d imeqqranen n řɛeskar d imnayen n iysan. \f ◼ \fr 2:9 \ft \+fk imnayen n iysan\ft  - niɣ ‘inni ineddhen iysan’.\f*   
\m
\v 10 \add Umi\add* Sanballaṭ zi Ḥurun, d Tubiya, amsexxar Aɛammuni, sřin aya, tuɣa aya ɣarsen d ict n tmesřact d taɛeffant aṭṭas, aqa yusa-dd ijj bnadem ḥima ad yarzu řxar i ayt n Israil.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Naḥamya ibda řxedmet nnes di Urcalim  
\m
\v 11 Ammu usiɣ-dd ɣar Urcalim uca dinni qqimeɣ třata n wussan.  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* kkareɣ di ǧiřet, necc d ca n yeryazen akidi, uca necc tuɣa war ssargbeɣ uřa d ijj n bnadem x min tuɣa d ayi igga SIDI deg wuř ḥima ad t ggeɣ i Urcalim, uca war kidi ksiɣ řmař mɣir řmař min xef i nyiɣ.  
\v 13 Ffɣeɣ s ǧiřet zi Tewwart n Teɣzurt ař udem n Tařa n Řhaycet u \add ssenni\add* ɣar Tewwart n Řeɣbar. Necc xemmeɣ řeḥyuḍ ittwarẓin n Urcalim i zi tiwwura nnes tecca i-tent tmessi.  
\v 14 Necc nedheɣ \add xenni\add* ɣar Tewwart n Tařa u ɣar Uyeřmam n ujeǧid, \add maca\add* war \add tuɣi\add* din ttasiɛ i řmař sadu inu ḥima ad arniɣ ɣar zzat.  
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* geɛɛdeɣ s ǧiřet x tseǧya uca xemmeɣ řḥiḍ uca ɛeqbeɣ-dd, uca udfeɣ ɛawed ɣar Tewwart n Teɣzurt. \add Ammu\add* i-dd-ɛeqbeɣ.   
\m
\v 16 War ssinen imḍebbaren mani tuɣa ruḥeɣ d min tuɣa xseɣ ad ggeɣ. Maɣar ař din war ssargbeɣ uřa d ict n řḥajjet i Wudayen d ikehhanen d tarwa n taṣiřet d imḍebbaren uřa i inneɣni inni iqqimen i řxedmet.  
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* nniɣ asen: “Kenniw tᵉttwařam řeɣben i di neǧa, aqa Urcalim tᵉttwaredeǧ u tiwwura nnes tecca i-tent tmessi. Asem-dd, ad nebna řḥiḍ n Urcalim, ḥima war nettwasseḥqar ɛad ktar.”  
\v 18 Necc ḥajiɣ asen mammec afus n SIDI inu tuɣa d aṣebḥan xafi uřa d awařen i d ayi inna ujeǧid. \add Xenni\add* nnan: “Neccin ad nekkar ad nebna.” Uca nitni ssjehden ifassen nsen i \add řxedmet-a\add* taṣebḥant   
\m
\v 19 \add Umi\add* sřin t Sanballaṭ, zi Ḥurun, d Ṭubiya, amsexxar zeg ayt n Ɛammun, d Weɛrab Jacam, ssthezzan zzayneɣ u sseḥqaren aneɣ. Nitni nnan: “Manawya min i da tᵉtteggem? Ma texsem ad tɣewwɣem x ujeǧid?”  
\v 20 Necc arriɣ-dd xasen, nniɣ asen: “AREBBI n ijenwan ad aneɣ iwc afus, u neccin, imsexxaren nnes, ad nekkar ad nebna. Kenniw \add maca\add* war ɣarwem bu tesɣart uřa d řḥeqq niɣ řidaret di Urcalim.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Řebni n řeḥyuḍ n Urcalim  
\m
\v 1 Arrays n ikehhanen, Ilyacib, ikkar, uřa d aytmas, ikehhanen, uca nitni ɛeddřen bnan Tawwart n Wuǧi, qeddsen tt uca ssbedden dayes tiwwura nnes. Nitni qeddsen uřa ticti ař Lburj n Mya u ař Lburj n Ḥananiyil.   
\m
\v 2 Ɣar uɣezdis nnes bnan yeryazen n Ariḥa uca ɣar uɣezdis nnes ibna Zakkur, mmis n Imri.   
\m
\v 3 Tawwart n Wesřem bnan tt ayt n Sana’a. Nitni arekkben tiḥenya n tzeqqa u ssbedden dayes tiwwura nnes ak-d zzekrunat nnes d iɛumad nnes i ubelleɛ.   
\m
\v 4 X uɣezdis nsen ibna Marimut, mmis n Uri-Yah, mmis n Haqquṣ, u ɣar uɣezdis nsen tuɣa iɛeddeř Macullam, mmis n Baraxya, mmis n Macizabyil u ɣar uɣezdis nsen iɛeddeř Ṣaduq, mmis n Baɛna.   
\m
\v 5 Ɣar uɣezdis nsen tuɣa ɛeddřen imezdaɣ n Taqquɛa, maca inni ɣar teǧa ṣṣulṭa jar asen war sseqwisen ca iri i řxedmet n SIDI nsen.   
\m
\v 6 Iɛeddeř Yuyadaɛ, mmis n Fasiḥ, ak-d Macullam, mmis n Basudya, Tawwart Taqdimt. Nitni arekkben tiḥenya n tzeqqa u ssbedden dayes tiwwura nnes ak-d zzekrunat nnes d iɛumad nnes i ubelleɛ.   
\m
\v 7 Ɣar uɣezdis nsen tuɣa iɛeddeř Malaṭya zi Jibɛun, d Yadun, Amiyarunuti, d yeryazen zi Jibɛun u zi Miṣfa ař mani tuɣa taddart n řkursi n lwali \add n temmurt\add* aɣirin i iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*.   
\m
\v 8 Ɣar uɣezdis nnes tuɣa iɛeddeř Ɛuzziyil, mmis n Ḥarhaya, ijjen zeg iḥeddaden n wureɣ, u ɣar uɣezdis nnes iɛeddeř Ḥananya, mmis n ijj zeg inni isswejden řeɛṭuř. Nitni jjin Urcalim ař řḥiḍ d miriw \add am t tuɣa\add*.   
\m
\v 9 Ɣar uɣezdis nsen tuɣa iɛeddeř Rafaya, mmis n Ḥur, ameqqran x wezyen n udewwar n Urcalim.  
\v 10 Ɣar uɣezdis nsen tuɣa iɛeddeř Yadaɛa, mmis n Ḥarumaf, ajemmaḍ n taddart nnes. U ɣar uɣezdis nnes tuɣa iɛeddeř Ḥattuc, mmis n Ḥacabniya.   
\b  
\m
\v 11 Malkiya, mmis n Ḥarim d Ḥaccub, mmis n Faḥat-Mu’ab ɛedřen tasɣart wiss tnayen uřa d Lburj n Tefqunt.   
\m
\v 12 Ɣar uɣezdis nnes tuɣa iɛeddeř Callum, mmis n Luḥic, ameqqran x wezyen nneɣni n udewwar n Urcalim, netta d yessis.   
\m
\v 13 Ḥanun d imezdaɣ n Zanuḥ ɛedřen Tawwart n Teɣzurt. Nitni arekkben tiḥenya u ssbedden dayes tiwwura nnes ak-d zzekrunat nnes d iɛumad nnes i ubelleɛ uca \add ɛedřen ɛawed\add* ařef n iɣaǧen n řḥiḍ ař Tewwart n Řeɣbar.   
\m
\v 14 Malkiya, mmis n Rakab, ameqqran n udewwar n Bayt-Karim, tuɣa iɛeddeř Tawwart n Řeɣbar. Netta yarekkeb tiḥenya u issbedd dayes tiwwura nnes ak-d zzekrunat nnes d iɛumad nnes i ubelleɛ.   
\b  
\m
\v 15 Callum, mmis n Kulhuz, ameqqran n udewwar Miṣfa, tuɣa iɛeddeř Tawwart n Tařa. Ibna i-tt u nitni arekkben tiḥenya n tzeqqa uca ssbedden dayes tiwwura nnes ak-d zzekrunat nnes d iɛumad nnes i ubelleɛ. \add Netta iɛdeř ɛawed\add* řḥiḍ zeg uyeřmam n Cilaḥ ɣar weḥwic n ujeǧid ař ddruj nni ihekkwan zi tendint n Dawud ɣar swadday. \f ◼ \fr 3:15 \ft \+fk ayeřmam n Cilah\ft  - ayeřmam-a ad taɣ d simant n uyeřmam am uyeřmam n Silwam, wenni aman nnes ffɣen zeg řɛunṣar n Jihun uca iwḍen ɣar uyeřmam n Silwam s qanat n Ḥizqiya tenni neqcen swadday i temmurt ɛřaḥař deg useggʷas 700 qbeř Lmasiḥ (xzar ɛawed Ica. 8:6).\f*   
\m
\v 16 Awarni as tuɣa iɛeddeř Naḥamya, mmis n Ɛazbuq, ameqqran n wezyen n udewwar n Bayt-Ṣur, ař ajemmaḍ i imeḍřan n Dawud u ař jjubb ittwaggen u ař Taddart n Ayt bu-teɣruḍt.   
\m
\v 17 Awarni as tuɣa ɛeddřen Ilawiyyen. Raḥum, mmis n Bani, \add u\add* ɣar uɣezdis nnes Ḥacabya, ameqqran n wezyen n udewwar n Qaɛila, deg udewwar nnes.   
\m
\v 18 Awarni as tuɣa ɛeddřen aytmatsen, Baway, mmis n Ḥinadad, ameqqran x wezyen nneɣni n udewwar n Qaɛila.   
\m
\v 19 Ɣar uɣezdis nnes tuɣa Ɛazir, mmis n Yecuɛa, ameqqran n Miṣfa, iɛeddeř ict n ṭṭarf nneɣni ajemmaḍ i tsawent ɣar \add taddart n\add* řesnaḥ, ɣar mani idewwar \add řḥiḍ\add*.   
\m
\v 20 Awarni as tuɣa Barux, mmis n Zabbay, iɛeddeř s cḍaret ijj n ṭṭarf nneɣni, zi mani ɣa idewwar \add řḥiḍ\add* ař tewwart n taddart n Ilyacib, arrays n ikehhanen.   
\m
\v 21 Awarni as tuɣa Marimut, mmis n Uriya, mmis n Haqquṣ, iɛeddeř ijj n ṭṭarf nneɣni, zi tewwart n taddart n Ilyacib ař aneggaru n taddart n Ilyacib.   
\m
\v 22 Awarni as tuɣa ɛeddřen ikehhanen. Nitni d iryazen zeg udewwar \add n L’Urdun\add*.   
\m
\v 23 Awarni asen tuɣa iɛeddeř Binyamin d Ḥaccub, ajemmaḍ i taddart nsen. Awarni asen tuɣa iɛeddeř Ɛazarya, mmis n Maɛasiya, mmis n Ɛananiya, zzat i taddart nnes.   
\m
\v 24 Awarni as tuɣa Binnuy, mmis n Ḥinadad, iɛeddeř ijj n ṭṭarf nneɣni, zi taddart n Ɛazarya ař mani ɣa idewwar \add řḥiḍ\add* ař taɣmart.   
\m
\v 25 Falal, mmis n Uzay, \add tuɣa iɛeddeř\add* ajemmaḍ mani ɣa idewwar \add řḥiḍ\add* d \add ujemmaḍ n\add* lburj yuɛřan wenni irefɛen x tzeddiɣt n sennej n ujeǧid, tenni ɣar zzat n řemraḥ n řeḥbes. Awarni as \add tuɣa iɛeddeř\add* Fadaya, mmis n Farɛuc.   
\m
\v 26 Imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant, inni tuɣa zeddɣen di Ɛufil, \add tuɣa ɛeddřen\add* ajemmaḍ i Tewwart n Waman ɣar ccarq u \add ɣar\add* lburj issewcen ɣar barra.   
\m
\v 27 Awarni as tuɣa imezdaɣ n Taqquɛa ɛeddřen ijj n ṭṭarf nneɣni ajemmaḍ i lburj ameqqran issewcen ɣar barra ař řḥiḍ n Ɛufil.   
\m
\v 28 Tuɣa ikehhanen ɛeddřen Tawwart n Iysan, kuř ijj ajemmaḍ i taddart nnes.   
\m
\v 29 Awarni asen tuɣa iɛeddeř Ṣaduq, mmis n Immir, ajemmaḍ i taddart nnes. U awarni as tuɣa iɛeddeř Camɛiya, mmis n Cakanya, aɛessas n Tewwart n Ccarq.   
\m
\v 30 Awarni as tuɣa Ḥananya, mmis n Calamya, d Ḥanun, mmis n Ṣalaf wiss setta, ɛeddřen ijj n ṭṭarf nneɣni. Awarni as tuɣa iɛeddeř Macullam, mmis n Baraxya, ajemmaḍ i texxamt nnes.   
\m
\v 31 Awarni as tuɣa iɛeddeř Malkiya, mmis n ijj n wemziř n wureɣ, ař taddart n imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant d isebbaben, ajemmaḍ i Tewwart n Řeḥsab u ař axxam n sennej ɣar teɣmart.   
\m
\v 32 Jar wexxam n sennej ɣar teɣmart d Tewwart n Wuǧi, tuɣa ɛeddřen imziřen n wureɣ d isebbaben.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řɛedyan war zemmaren ad ssbedden řxedmet  
\m
\v 33 Umi Sanballaṭ isřa, aqa nbenna řḥiḍ, imsar aqa ihaj, isɛar aṭṭas uca issbehdeř Udayen.   
\m
\v 34 Tuɣa issawař jar aytmas d řɛeskar n Samarya, inna: “Min tteggen Wudayen-a iḍeɛfen? Ma ad ten nejj? Ma ad qedmmen tiɣarṣa? Ma ad \add t\add* kemmřen deg ijj n wass? Ma ad ssekkaren \add ɛawed\add* iẓra zi arwinat inni ittwacemḍen?”  
\v 35 \add Tuɣa\add* Ṭubiya, zeg ayt n Ɛammun, akides, inna: “Ɛad mařa bnan t ɛawed, xmi ɣa iffeɣ ijj n wecɛeb \add waha\add*, xenni ad ihdem řḥiḍ nsen n weẓru.”   
\b  
\m
\v 36 “Seř, a AREBBI nneɣ, mammec i nedweř nettwasseḥqar uca arr aseḥqar nsen x uzeǧif nsen uca sellem i-ten d takeccaḍt ɣar ict n temmurt n uḥebbes.  
\v 37 War sduriy řmuɛṣiyyet nsen u war ttejji ad ittwamḥa ddnub nsen zzat i wudem nnec, minzi nitni sɛaren Cek qibač i ibennayen.”   
\m
\v 38 Nebna řḥiḍ, ařami idweř řḥiḍ iqqen ař azyen, minzi řgens igga uř nsen ad t ggen. *   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\m
\v 1 Umi \add maca\add* Sanballaṭ d Ṭubiya d Weɛraben d ayt n Ɛammun d Icdudiyyen sřan, aqa aɛdař n řeḥyuḍ n Urcalim ittraḥ ɣar zzat, tizzeyyin bdant ad qqnent, imsar, aqa xeyyqen aṭṭas.  
\v 2 Nitni marra ggin tameɛmuč maḥend ad dd-asen ad mmenɣen ak-d Urcalim, ad dinni ssekkaren řeḥweř. \x ◘ \xo 4:2 \xt Izhd. 2\x*  
\v 3 Neccin \add maca\add* nẓuǧ ɣar AREBBI nneɣ u di ssibbet nsen nessbedd ict n tɛessast xasen ass d ǧiřet.   
\m
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* inna Yahuda: “Jjhed n yinni yarebbun yuḥeř, maɣar din aṭṭas n řxarbet. War nzemmar x řebni n řḥiḍ.”  
\v 5 Iɣrimen nneɣ aqa nnan: “Nitni war tticin u war ttwiřin walu ař dd ɣa nas di řwesṭ nsen u ad ten neneɣ. \add Ammu\add* i ɣa nessbedd řxedmet.   
\m
\v 6 Řami dd-usin Wudayen, inni ɣarsen izeddɣen, nnan aneɣ ɛecra n twařawin: “Ittxeṣṣa kenniw ad ɣarneɣ dd-tɛeqbem!”,   
\m
\v 7 ssbeddeɣ necc řgens awarni i řḥiḍ ɣar imucan iwaṭan u ɣar tseqqar ifruren, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, ak-d řesyuf nsen d iḥricen nsen d řeqwas nsen. \f ◼ \fr 4:7 \ft \+fk řesyuf\ft  - niɣ ‘ijenyan’.\f*  
\v 8 Xzareɣ, \add xenni\add* kkareɣ, nniɣ i tarwa n taṣiřet u i imḍebbaren u i min iqqimen n řgens: “War zzaysen tteggʷedem ca! Sidi inu d ameqqran u issaggʷad. Fekkarem dayes, mmenɣem i aytmatwem, iḥenjiren nwem d tḥenjirin nwem d temɣarin nwem d tudrin nwem.”   
\m
\v 9 Umi sřan řɛedyan nneɣ, aqa \add neccin\add* nargeb xas u aqa AREBBI ibḍeř anway nsen, imsar xenni neccin marra idneɣ neɛqeb ɣar řḥiḍ, kuř ijj ɣar wemcan \add nnes\add*.  
\v 10 Zeg wass nni imsar, aqa azyen n imsexxaren inu tuɣa xeddmen u azyen nneɣni zzaysen ṭṭfen iḥricen d tseddariyin \add n uɛeskari\add* d řeqwas d warruḍ n wuzzař, uca řḥukkam \add bedden\add* awarni i kuř taddart n Yahuda.  
\v 11 Inni tuɣa ittbennan řḥiḍ uca yarebbun ddquřat uca ssarebbun tent, xeddmen s yijj n ufus u s \add ufus\add* nneɣni ṭṭfen lansa.  
\v 12 \add Marra\add* inni tuɣa ibennan aqa ɣarsen ssif iqqen x tejɛinna nnes am tuɣa ibenna. Wenni ittsuḍen deg uyicc n icarri, tuɣa-t akidi.   
\m
\v 13 Nniɣ i tarwa n taṣiřet u i imḍebbaren u i min iqqimen n řgens: “Řxedmet temɣar u teyru. Neccin nettwabezzeɛ x řḥiḍ, ijjen iggʷej x wenneɣni.  
\v 14 Deg wemcan mani ɣa tesřem asuḍi deg uyicc n icarri, munem-dd dinni xaneɣ. AREBBI nneɣ ad immneɣ di ṭṭweɛ nneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 4:14 \xt Uf. 14:25; Aɛwd. 1:30; 28:7\x*   
\m
\v 15 Ammu i nexdem uca azyen zzaysen ṭṭfen iḥricen zi tuffut ař dd ɣa ffɣen itran.  
\v 16 Di řweqt nni nniɣ i řgens: “Kuř ijj ad issens daxeř di Urcalim ak-d umsexxar nnes uca ammu i ɣarneɣ i ɣa yiřin d iɛessasen di ǧiřet u deg wass \add ad iřin i\add* řxedmet.”  
\v 17 Uřa d ijj zzayneɣ war ikkis arruḍ, war iǧi necc řa d aytma řa d imsexxaren inu uřa d yeryazen n tɛessast. Kuř ijj \add iruḥ ɣar\add* waman ak-d lansa nnes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\s1 Naḥamya iwca afus i imeẓřaḍ  
\m
\v 1 Ikkar ijj n uɣuyyi imɣar n řgens u n temɣarin nsen, \add cetcan nitni\add* x aytmatsent, Udayen.  
\v 2 Aqa din inni innan: “Iḥenjiren nneɣ d tḥenjirin nneɣ d neccin d aṭṭas. Ittxeṣṣa ad nseɣ imendi ḥima ad necc ad neddar.”  
\v 3 Inneɣni nnan: “Neccin narhen iyyaren nneɣ d imarjaɛen nneɣ n uḍiř d tudrin nneɣ d aḍman, ḥima ad nawi řḥebb \add n yirden\add* deg \add wussan n\add* řaẓ.”  
\v 4 \add Inneɣni\add* nnan: “Neccin narḍeř nnuqart i ljizya i ujeǧid x iyyaren nneɣ u x imarjaɛen nneɣ n uḍiř.”  
\v 5 “Xenni řexxu, aysum nneɣ d aysum n aytmatneɣ, iḥenjiren nneɣ am iḥenjiren nsen, u xzar, iḥenjiren nneɣ d tḥenjirin nneɣ ittxeṣṣa aneɣ ad ten narr d isemɣan. Aqa din zi yessitneɣ tinni idewřen am tseɣmin, uca afus nneɣ war izemmar \add ad igg ca\add* u iyyaren nneɣ d imarjaɛen nneɣ n uḍiř aqa deg ufus n inneɣni.”   
\m
\v 6 Umi sřiɣ iɣuyyan nsen d wawařen-a, dewřeɣ xeyyqeɣ aṭṭas.  
\v 7 Necc xarrṣeɣ deg wuř inu u \add xenni\add* cetciɣ x tarwa n taṣiřet u x imḍebbaren, nniɣ asen: “Kuř ijj zzaywem dayes řɛib umi igga amarwas deg umas.” Necc ggiɣ ijj n wegraw d ameqqran ḍidd nsen. \x ◘ \xo 5:7 \xt Uf. 22:24\x*  
\v 8 Necc nniɣ asen: “Neccin nesɣa aytmatneɣ, Udayen, inni tuɣa ittwazzenzen i řegnus, ɛlaḥsab tizemmar nneɣ. Ma texsem ad tezzenzem \add ɛawed\add* tawmatwem u ttwammesɣen nitni zzayneɣ \add ɛawed\add*?” Uca sseɣden war ufin min ɣa inin.  
\v 9 \add Xas uca\add* nniɣ: “Min tᵉtteggem kenniw, war iǧi nican. Ma war ittxeṣṣi ad tuyurem zzat i AREBBI nneɣ s uweqqar zi ssibbet n useḥqar n řegnus, řɛedyan nneɣ?  
\v 10 Uřa d necc, aytma d imsexxaren inu, aqa narḍer asen nnuqart d imendi. Jjem aneɣ ad nesmeḥ maca deg umarwas-a.  
\v 11 Arrem asen ass-a iyyaren nsen, imarjaɛen nsen n uḍiř, řeɛraṣit nsen n zzitun d tudrin nsen uca semḥen asen di tasɣart wiss mya n nnuqart d imendi d binu n jdid d zzect nni i zzaysen tᵉttᵉttarem \add ɛad\add*.”  
\v 12 \add Xas uca\add* nnan: “Ad asen t narr marra u war zzaysen t nᵉttettar \add ɛad\add*. Neccin ad negg, am mammec tennid cek.” Uca řaɣiɣ i ikehhanen u jjiɣ ten ad jjaǧen, aqa nitni ad ggen ɛlaḥsab awař-a.  
\v 13 Xenni zzerzeɣ weḥsin n warruḍ inu, nniɣ: “Ammu i ɣa izzerz AREBBI kuř aryaz nni war iṭṭifen deg wawař-a, zi taddart nnes u zeg wagřa nnes, \add wah,\add* iři ad t zzerzen ařami i ɣa ixwa.” Agraw \add n řgens\add* marra inna: “Amin!” Nitni ssemɣaren SIDI d řgens i iggin ɛlaḥsab awař-a. \f ◼ \fr 5:13 \ft \+fk aḥsin\ft  - niɣ ‘abeḥrur’.\f*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Amedya n Naḥamya  
\m
\v 14 Uřa d necc d yaytma war necci ca macca n ijj n lwali zeg wass nni di i d ayi igga d lwali nsen di temmurt n Yahuda, zeg useggʷas wiss ɛicrin ař aseggʷas wiss tnayen u-třatin n ujeǧid Artaḥcasta, \add teqqar\add* tenɛac n iseggʷusa.  
\v 15 Lwulat nni din iǧan qbeř i necc, tuɣa ggin ddqeř x řgens u tuɣa ksin zzayes aɣrum d binu u ɛawed arebɛin ciqlu n nnuqart. Uřa d imsexxaren nsen seǧḍen x řgens. Necc maca war ggiɣ aya zi tiggʷudi n AREBBI.  
\v 16 Aqa wciɣ jjehd inu i řxedmet ɣar řḥiḍ u neccin war nesɣi ca aḥwic u marra imsexxaren munen din x řxedmet.  
\v 17 Ɣar ṭṭabřa inu \add qqimen\add* mya u-xemsin n yeryazen zeg Wudayen u zeg imḍebbaren uřa d inni i ɣarneɣ dd-yusin zi řegnus i d aneɣ dd-innḍen.  
\v 18 Min ittwasswejden ayi i yijj n wass, aqa d ijj n ufunas, setta n texsiwin ittwafarzen zeg wuǧi uřa d ijḍaḍ, u di kuř ɛecra n wussan ɛřam kuř binu s ufeyyeḍ. S marra aya war ttareɣ macca n lwali, maɣar tasexxart tessedqeř aṭṭas x řgens-a.  
\v 19 Idar ayi s řxar, \add a\add* AREBBI inu, s marra min ggiɣ i řgens-a. \x ◘ \xo 5:19 \xt Naḥ. 13:22\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\s1 Akemmeř n řḥiḍ  
\m
\v 1 Umi xebbaren i Sanballaṭ d Ṭubiya d Weɛrab Jacam d řɛedyan nneɣni, aqa necc bniɣ řḥiḍ ɛawed u war tuɣi dayes teqqim tazzit \add ɛad\add*, aqa zeɛma necc tuɣa ayi ɛad war arekkbeɣ tiwwura, \add xenni\add* imsar,  
\v 2 aqa Sanballaṭ d Jacam ssekken-dd ɣari \add řexbar\add*, nnan: “As-dd, ad nemmẓar di dcurat di řewḍa n Unu.” Nitni maca tuɣa nwan ad ggen taɛeffant akidi.  
\v 3 Necc ssekkeɣ ɣarsen ireqqasen ad inin: “Necc xeddmeɣ řexxu di řxedmet d tameqqrant, x uya war zemmareɣ ad dd-aseɣ. Mayemmi ɣa tbedd řxedmet-a mařa jjiɣ tt, hwiɣ-dd ɣarwem?”  
\v 4 Nitni ssekken ayi-dd tabrat-a arebɛa n twařawin u necc arriɣ-dd xasen \add řebda\add* s webrid d ijjen.  
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* issekk-dd ɣari Sanballaṭ řexbar-a i twařa wiss xemsa. Amsexxar nnes \add tuɣa ɣares\add* ict n tebrat tarzmen s ufus nnes,  
\v 6 yura dayes: “Aqa idweř ittwassen jar řegnus u Jacmu iqqar: ‘Cek d Wudayen texsem ad tɣewwɣem. X uya tessbeddem řḥiḍ!’, u cek texsed ad tdewřed d ajeǧid nsen x řeḥsab awařen-a.” \f ◼ \fr 6:6 \ft \+fk Jacmu\ft  - niɣ ‘Jacam’ (xzar nnumra 2).\f*  
\v 7 Cek ɛawed tařeqmed inabiyyen, maḥend ad xak dd-barrḥen di Urcalim, ad inin: ‘Netta d ajeǧid di Yahuda!’ Awařen-a ad awḍen maca i ujeǧid. S uya as-dd řexxu, ad nemcawar.”  
\v 8 Necc \add maca\add* ssekkeɣ as \add tabrat\add* maḥend ad as iniɣ: “Timesřayin-a i tennid, war ǧint ca d tidett, maca cek teggid tent deg wuř nnec.”  
\v 9 Minzi nitni marra xsen ad aneɣ ssiggʷden, nnan: “Nitni ad kksen ifassen nsen zi řxedmet, maḥend war tt tteggen.” Xenni řexxu, sejhed ifassen inu!   
\m
\v 10 Necc udfeɣ ɣar taddart n Camɛiya, mmis n Dalaya, mmis n Mahiṭab’il. Netta tuɣa ibelleɛ x ixef nnes dinni, inna: “Ejj aneɣ ad nmun di Taddart n AREBBI, di řwesṭ n Zzawect, ad nbelleɛ tiwwura n Zzawect Tameqqrant, maɣar ad dd-asen nitni, ḥima ad cek nɣen, \add wah,\add* ad dd-asen di ǧiřet ḥima ad cek nɣen.”  
\v 11 \add Maca\add* necc nniɣ: “Ma necc d ijj n weryaz i tarewřa? Ma ijjen am necc ad yadef ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant uca ad iqqim iddar? War tt ttadfeɣ.”  
\v 12 \add Minzi\add* argbeɣ u ẓriɣ, aqa war iǧi d AREBBI i tuɣa t-i-dd-issekken, maca netta issiweř ak-d nnubuwa-ya xafi, minzi Ṭubiya d Sanballaṭ tuɣa cran t.  
\v 13 Tuɣa cran t, maḥend ad ggʷedeɣ ad ggeɣ amenni uca ad xḍiɣ, maḥend ad ɣarsen yiři ca i zi dayi i ɣa ggen isem d aɛeffan, ḥima ad ayi ɛeyyaren.  
\v 14 \add A\add* SIDI inu, idar i Ṭubiya d Sanballaṭ, min ggin, uřa d tanabit Nuɛadya d inabiyyen nneɣni inni tuɣa yarezzun ad ayi ssiggʷden.  
\v 15 Ittwakemmeř řḥiḍ awarni i tnayen u-xemsin n wussan, deg \add wass\add* wiss xemsa u-ɛicrin n \add uyur n\add* Ilul.  
\v 16 Umi sřin marra řɛedyan nneɣ man aya, uca uřa d marra řegnus i d aneɣ dd-innḍen ẓrin t, dewřen nitni d imuqřiřen di tiṭṭawin n yixef nsen, ucin aqa d AREBBI i tuɣa iggin řxedmet-a.   
\m
\v 17 Deg wussan nni urin tarwa n taṣiřet n Yahuda aṭṭas n tebratin, sekken tent i Ṭubiya uca aqa din uřa d tinni iffɣen zi Ṭubiya ɣarsen.  
\v 18 Maɣar aṭṭas di Yahuda tuɣa jjuǧen as, maɣar netta tuɣa d aḍeggʷař n Caxanya, mmis n Araḥ, u mmis \add nnes\add* Yuḥanan tuɣa yiwi yeǧis n Macullam, mmis n Baraxya, d tamɣart.  
\v 19 Ɛawed ssiwřen zzat i wudem inu x tmegga nnes tiṣebḥanin u ssiwḍen awařen inu ɣares. U Ṭubiya tuɣa i d ayi dd-issekkan tibratin ḥima ad ayi issiggʷed.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\s1 Taɛessast n tendint  
\m
\v 1 Umi ittwassbedd řḥiḍ ɛawed u ggiɣ tiwwura ad ttwarekkbent, aqa řeqqmeɣ iɛessasen n tewwura d imedyazen d Ilawiyyen. \f ◼ \fr 7:1 \ft \+fk imedyazen\ft  - niɣ ‘imeɣnujen’.\f*  
\v 2 Necc umureɣ i uma Ḥanani u i Ḥananya, ameqqran n lqelɛa di Urcalim, minzi netta d ijj n weryaz d amtiqqi, itteggʷed AREBBI ktar x waṭṭas \add inneɣni\add*.  
\v 3 Necc nniɣ asen: “War ttnurziment tewwura n Urcalim ař ɣa tezweɣ tfuct uca jjem ad bellɛen tiwwura u ad arren izekrunen umi nitni bedden ɛad \add i tɛessast\add*. Ittxeṣṣa ad ggen iɛessasen zeg imezdaɣ n Urcalim, kuř ijj deg wemcan n tɛessast nnes u kuř ijj qibač i taddart nnes.  
\v 4 Tuɣa tandint tennejbed u temɣar, \add maca\add* tuɣa dayes řgens drus u tudrin tuɣa war bnint \add ɛad\add*.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Lista n yenni iɛeqben zi tmeḥbast ak-d Zarubbabil  
\m
\v 5 Igga AREBBI deg wuř inu ad řaɣiɣ i tarwa n taṣiřet d imḍebbaren ḥima ad yiři ijj n uzemmem n \add řgens\add* uca ufiɣ lista n jjadira n yinni dd-igeɛɛden d amezwaru, ufiɣ yura dayes \add man aya\add*:   
\b  
\m
\v 6 “Aqa d ina d ayt n lɛamala nni dd-igeɛɛden zi tmeḥbast - imenfiyyen nni dd-iwyi Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, di lmenfa - uca ɛeqben ɣar Urcalim d Yahuda, kuř ijj ɣar tendint nnes, \x ◘ \xo 7:6 \xt Ɛiz. 2\x*  
\v 7 inni dd-yusin ak-d Zarubbabil, Yahucaɛ, Naḥamya, Ɛazarya, Raɛamya, Naḥamani, Murdaxay, Bilcan, Misfarat, Biɣway, Naḥum d Baɛna.  
\m Wa d \bd řqedd n yeryazen n řgens n Israil.\bd* \f ◼ \fr 7:7 \ft \+fk řqedd\ft  - niɣ ‘lɛadad’ niɣ ‘amdan’.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 8 Ayt n Farɛuc: ařfayen u-mya u-tnayen u-sebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 9 Ayt n Cafaṭya: teřt-mya u-tnayen u-sebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 10 Ayt n Araḥ: setta-mya u-tnayen u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 11 Ayt n Fahat-Mu’ab, zeg ayt n Yecuɛa d Yuwab: ařfayen u-tmenya-mya u-tmenya-ɛecra \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 12 Ayt n Ɛilam: ařef u-mitayn u-arebɛa u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 13 Ayt n Zattu: temn-mya u-xemsa u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 14 Ayt n Zakkay: sebɛa-mya u-settin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 15 Ayt n Binnay: setta-mya u-tmenya u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 16 Ayt n Babay: setta-mya u-tmenya u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 17 Ayt n Ɛarjad: ařfayen u-ṭert-mya u-tnayen u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 18 Ayt n Aduniqam: setta-mya u-sebɛa u-settin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 19 Ayt n Biɣway: ařfayen u-sebɛa u-settin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 20 Ayt n Ɛadin: setta-mya u-xemsa u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 21 Ayt n Aṭir zi Ḥizqiya: tmenya u-tesɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 22 Ayt n Ḥacum: teřt-mya u-tmenya u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 23 Ayt n Biṣay: teřt-mya u-arebɛa u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 24 Ayt n Ḥarif: mya u-tenɛac \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 25 Ayt n Jibɛun: xemsa u-tesɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 26 Iryazen n Bayt-Laḥm d Naṭufa: mya u-tmenya u-tmanyin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 27 Iryazen n Ɛanatut: mya u-tmenya u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 28 Iryazen n Bayt-Ɛazmut: tnayen u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 29 Iryazen n Qaryat-Yaɛarim, Kafira d Biɛrut: sebɛa-mya u-třata u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 30 Iryazen n Rama d Jabaɛ: setta-mya u-waḥed u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 31 Iryazen n Mixmas: mya u-tnayen u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 32 Iryazen n Bayt-Il d Ɛay: mya u-třata u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 33 Iryazen n Nabu nneɣni: tnayen u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 34 Ayt n ijj n Ɛilam nneɣni, ařef u-mitayn u-arebɛa u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 35 Ayt n Ḥarim: teřt-mya u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 36 Ayt n Ariḥa: teřt-mya u-xemsa u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 37 Ayt n Lud, Ḥadid d Unu: sebɛa-mya u-waḥed u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 38 Ayt n Sana’a: teřt-ařaf u-tesɛa-mya u-třatin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\b  
\m
\v 39 \bd Ikehhanen.\bd*  
\m Ayt n Yadaɛya, zi taddart n Yecuɛa: tesɛa-mya u-třata u-sebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 40 Ayt n Immir: ařef u-tnayen u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 41 Ayt n Facḥur: ařef u-mitayn u-sebɛa u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 42 Ayt n Ḥarim: ařef u-sbeɛṭac \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\b  
\m
\v 43 \bd Ilawiyyen.\bd*  
\m Ayt n Yecuɛa, ayt n Qadmiyil, zeg ayt n Huduwya: arebɛa u-sebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\b  
\m
\v 44 \bd Imedyazen.\bd*  
\m Ayt n Asaf: mya u-tmenya u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\b  
\m
\v 45 \bd Ayt n iɛessasen n tewwura.\bd*  
\m Ayt n Callum, ayt n Aṭir, ayt n Ṭalmun, ayt n Ɛaqqub, ayt n Ḥaṭiṭa, ayt n Cubay, aqa aten \add jmiɛ\add*: mya u-tmenya u-třatin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\b  
\m
\v 46 \bd Imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant.\bd*  
\m Ayt n Ṣiḥa, ayt n Ḥasufa, ayt n Ṭabaɛut,   
\m
\v 47 ayt n Qiruc, ayt n Ciɛa, ayt n Fadun,   
\m
\v 48 ayt n Labana, ayt n Ḥajaba, ayt n Salmay,   
\m
\v 49 ayt n Ḥanan, ayt n Jadil, ayt n Ḥajar,   
\m
\v 50 ayt n Ra’aya, ayt n Raṣin, ayt n Naqquda,   
\m
\v 51 ayt n Jazzam, ayt n Ɛazza, ayt n Fasiḥ,   
\m
\v 52 ayt n Bisay, ayt n Maɛunim, ayt n Naficasim,   
\m
\v 53 ayt n Baqbuq, ayt n Ḥaqufa, ayt n Ḥarḥur,   
\m
\v 54 ayt n Baṣlit, ayt n Maḥida, ayt n Ḥarca,   
\m
\v 55 ayt n Barqus, ayt n Sisara, ayt n Tamaḥ,   
\m
\v 56 ayt n Naṣiḥ, ayt n Ḥaṭifa,   
\b  
\m
\v 57 \bd Ayt n imsexxaren n Suliman.\bd*  
\m Ayt n Suṭay, ayt n Sufarat, ayt n Farida,   
\m
\v 58 ayt n Yaɛla, ayt n Darqun, ayt n Jiddil,   
\m
\v 59 ayt n Cafaṭya, ayt n Ḥattil, ayt n Fuxarat-ha-Ḍabayim d ayt n Amun.   
\b  
\m
\v 60 Marra imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant d ayt n imsexxaren n Suliman, aqa aten \add jmiɛ\add* teřt-mya u-tnayen u-tesɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\b  
\m
\v 61 Ina d inni igeɛɛden zi Tal-Milḥ, Tal-Ḥarca, Karub, Addan d Immir, \add maca\add* nitni war zemmaren ad ssecnen zi jjihet n taddart n řejdud nsen niɣ zi jjihet n zzariɛet nsen, aqa nitni \add ffɣen\add* zi Israil:  
\v 62 ayt n Dalaya, ayt n Ṭubiya, ayt n Naqquda: setta-mya u-tnayen u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 63 Uca zeg ikehhanen: ayt n Ḥabaya, ayt n Haqquṣ, ayt n Barzillay, \add aqa zzaysen wenni\add* iwyen ict n temɣart zi yessis n Ujilɛadi Barzillay u ittwařaɣa s yisem nsen.   
\m
\v 64 Nitni arzun x tewriqt n uzemmem nsen \add di lista n jjadira\add*, maca war tt ufin. S uyenni ttwassuffɣen nitni zi tukehhant.  
\v 65 Lwali ameqqran inna asen, war ttᵉtten zi tmesřayin iqeddsen qaɛ ař ɣa ikkar ijj n ukehhan ak-d Urim d Tummim.   
\b  
\m
\v 66 Marra agraw \add n řgens\add* \add tuɣa di\add* tnayen u-rebɛin-ařef u-teřt-mya u-settin \add n yeryazen\add*,   
\m
\v 67 nhřa isemɣan nsen d tiyya nsen, \add maɣar\add* ina tuɣa aten marra sebɛa-ařaf u-teřt-mya u-sebɛa u-třatin, uca ɣarsen mitayen u-xemsa u-rebɛin n imedyazen d tmedyazin.   
\m
\v 68 Iřeɣman nsen \add tuɣa aten di\add* arebɛa-mya u-xemsa u-třatin \add u\add* iɣyař nsen \add tuɣa aten di\add* setta-ařaf u-sebɛa-mya u-ɛicrin.   
\m
\v 69 Ca zeg izeǧifen x ibabaten \add n řaǧat\add* wcin i řxedmet. Lwali ameqqran iwca i ssenduq n txubay \add n řxedmet\add* ařef n draxmat n wureɣ d xemsin n ṭṭawyat i urucci d xemsa-mya u-třatin n tcamirat i ikehhanen. \f ◼ \fr 7:69 \ft \+fk tixubay\ft  - niɣ ‘řeknuz’.\f*   
\m
\v 70 Ca nneɣni zeg izeǧifen x ibabaten \add n řaǧat\add* wcin i ssenduq n txubay i řxedmet ɛicrin-ařef n draxmat n wureɣ d ařfayen n minayat n nnuqart.   
\m
\v 71 Uca min iqqimen zi řgens iwca ɛicrin-ařef n draxmat n wureɣ d ařfayen n minayat n nnuqart d sebɛa u-settin n tcamirat i ikehhanen.   
\m
\v 72 Ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen d iɛessasen n tewwart d imedyazen d ca zi řgens d imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant uřa d marra Israil, \add marra nitni\add* ggin ad zedɣen di tneddam nsen.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 8
\s1 Taɣuri i řgens zi Ccariɛa n Musa  
\m
\v 1 \add Umi\add* ibda uyur wiss sebɛa uca tuɣa ayt n Israil di tneddam nsen, imun marra řgens am yijj n weryaz deg wazzay n Tewwart n Waman, nnan i Ɛizra, amseřmed n Ccariɛa, ad yawi adlis n Ccariɛa n Musa, tenni yumur SIDI i Israil.  
\v 2 Deg wass amezwaru n uyur wiss sebɛa yiwi-dd ukehhan Ɛizra Ccariɛa zzat i wudem n wegraw \add n řgens\add* wenni \add iǧan\add* zeg yeryazen d temɣarin d marra inni izemmaren ad as fehmem xmi i d as i ɣa sřen.  
\v 3 Netta iɣra zzayes ɣar wudem n wazzay \add i iǧan\add* zzat i Tewwart n Waman, zi tuffut ař azyen n wass, i yeryazen d temɣarin d inni izemmaren ad as fehmem. Tuɣa imezzuɣen n marra řgens ɣar wedlis ittwannḍen n Ccariɛa.  
\v 4 Uca Ɛizra, amseřmad n idlisen, ibedd x ijj n ddruj n ukeccuḍ nni ggin nitni i uya, u x uɣezdis nnes afusi bedden Mattitya d Camaɛ d Ɛanaya d Uriya d Ḥilqiya d Maɛasiya u x uzeřmaḍ nnes \add bedden\add* Fadaya d Micayil d Malkiya d Ḥacum d Ḥacbaddana, Zakariyya d Macullam.  
\v 5 Yarzem Ɛizra adlis zzat i tiṭṭawin n marra řgens, maɣar ibedd sennej i marra řgens uca umi t yarzem, ikkar-dd řgens marra.   
\m
\v 6 Ɛizra issemɣar SIDI, AREBBI d ameqqran, uca řgens yarra-dd s ifassen nsen ɣar ujenna: “Amin, amin!” Uca nitni yuḍaren, bendqen i SIDI s uɣembub \add nsen\add* ɣar temmurt.  
\v 7 Ssřemden Yecuɛa, Bani, Carabya, Yamin, Ɛaqqub, Cabbatay, Hudiya, Maɛasiya, Qaliṭa, Ɛazarya, Yuzabad, Ḥanan, Falaya d Ilawiyyen řgens di Ccariɛa u řgens \add iqqim\add* deg wemcan nnes.  
\v 8 Ɣrin nitni zeg wedlis ittwannḍen, zi Ccariɛa n AREBBI, carrḥen u ssecnen řmeɛna i daysen uca ammu i ssfehmen min ittwaɣrin.  
\v 9 Uca Naḥamya, wenni d lwali ameqqran, d ukehhan Ɛizra, amseřmad, d Ilawiyyen inni issřemden řgens, nnan i marra řgens: “Ass-a d amqeddes i SIDI, AREBBI nwem. War ccatem agejdur, war ttrum.” Minzi marra řgens tuɣa iru umi sřan awařen n Ccariɛa.  
\v 10 Inna asen \add ɛawed\add*: “Uyurem u teccem \add macca isswejden\add* s waṭṭas n zzect, sswem binu amiẓid uca wcem macca i wenni war d as sswejden walu, maɣar ass-a d ijj n wass d amqeddes i Siditneɣ. War sḥissifem, maɣar řefraḥet n SIDI d lqelɛa nwem.  
\v 11 Ilawiyyen ssfewwjen marra řgens, nnan: “Sqarem, maɣar ass-a d amqeddes \add i iǧa\add*. War sḥissifem ca!”  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* yuyur marra řgens ḥima ad ccen ad swen u ad ṣedqen u ḥima ad farḥen s waṭṭas, minzi nitni fehmen i wawařen i d asen ittwannan.  
\v 13 Tiwecca nnes munen izeǧifen x ibabaten \add n řaǧat\add* n marra řgens d ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen ɣar Ɛizra, amseřmad n idlisen, ḥima ad arzun řefhamet deg wawařen n Ccariɛa.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Aɛeyyed n Řɛid n Iɛuccuten  
\m
\v 14 Nitni ufin belli tura di Ccariɛa, aqa SIDI yumur s tsexxart n Musa, ittxeṣṣa i ayt n Israil ad zedɣen deg iɛuccuten di Řɛid deg uyur wiss sebɛa, \x ◘ \xo 8:14 \xt Uf. 23:16; Lawi 23:34; Řxř. 29:12-39; Aɛwd. 16:13, 14, 15\x*  
\v 15 u ittxeṣṣa asen ad zzayes barrḥen uca ad sseɛdun ijj n uřaɣi di marra tineddam nsen uřa di Urcalim ḥima ad inin: “Fɣem ɣar idurar u awyem-dd ifetwan n tcejjura n zzitun d ifetwan n izemmuren d ifetwan n tariḥant d ifetwan n tcejjart n tini d ifetwan n marra ticejjura ɣarsent tifray, maḥend ad zzaysen teggem iɛuccuten, am mammec \add tt\add* tura.”  
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ-dd řgens ɣar barra, iwyen-dd \add ifetwan\add* uca ggin i yixef nsen iɛuccuten, kuř ijj x tzeqqa nnes u di řemraḥat nsen u di řemraḥat n Taddart n AREBBI u deg wazzay n Tewwart n Waman u deg wazzay n Tewwart n Ifrayim.   
\m
\v 17 Marra agraw \add n řgens\add* n yinni dd-iɛeqben zi tmeḥbast, ggin iɛuccuten u zeddɣen deg iɛuccuten minzi ayt n Israil war ggin aya zeg wussan n Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, ař ass-a uca řefraḥet tuɣa-tt d tameqqrant aṭṭas.  
\v 18 Ass iḍfar umas ittwaɣra \add xasen\add* zeg wedlis ittwannḍen n Ccariɛa n AREBBI, zeg wass amezwaru ař ass aneggaru. Ammu i ɛeyyden řmijař n sebɛa n wussan u deg wass wiss tmenya \add tuɣa din\add* ijj n umuni ifarzen am mammec i teǧa di lfariḍa.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 9
\s1 Ass n ttubet d tẓaǧit  
\m
\v 1 Deg wass wiss arebɛa u-ɛicrin n uyur-a munen ayt n Israil s uẓummi u \add řeḥḥfen\add* deg warruḍ n txuncay \add n wecḍan\add* u s tɛejjajt \add x uzeǧif\add*. \f ◼ \fr 9:1 \ft \+fk deg warruḍ n wecḍan\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘s txancet’. \fk taɛejjact\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘acař’.\f*  
\v 2 Bḍan zzariɛet n Israil ixef nsen zi marra ibarraniyyen, uca am qqimen kkaren, neɛmen zi ddnub nsen d řmuɛṣiyyet n řejdud nsen.  
\v 3 \add Xas uca\add* dewřen bedden deg wemcan nsen \add ɛawed\add* uca ɣrin asen ict n terbaɛt n wass zeg wedlis ittwannḍen n Ccariɛa n SIDI, AREBBI nsen, uca ict n terbaɛt nneɣni neɛmen nitni \add s ddnub nsen\add* uca sejden i SIDI, AREBBI nsen.  
\v 4 X ddruj n Ilawiyyen ibedd Yecuɛa d Bani, Qadmiyil, Cabanya, Bunni, Carabya, Bani d Kanani, řaɣan s tmijja ijehden ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nsen.  
\v 5 Uca Ilawiyyen, Yecuɛa, Qadmiyil, Bani, Ḥacabniya, Carabya, Hudiya, Cabanya \add d\add* Fataḥya, nnan: “Kkarem, tbarkem SIDI, AREBBI nwem, zi řebda ař řebda! Iři ad ittwabarek Isem n uɛuǧi nnec, wenni yuɛřan x marra lbaraka d usemɣar!”   
\b  
\m
\v 6 “Cek d SIDI, mɣir Cek. Cek teggid ajenna uřa d ajenna n ijenwan d marra tizemmar nsen, tammurt d marra min xas \add iǧan\add*, řebḥur d marra min dayes \add iǧan\add* u Cek tewcid asen tudart uca řɛeskarat n ujenna ttbendaqent i Cek. \x ◘ \xo 9:6 \xt Amz. 1; Izhd. 146:6; Řex. 14:15; 17:24; Asa. 14:7\x*   
\m
\v 7 Cek d SIDI, AREBBI, wenni ifarzen Abram. Cek tessuffɣed t-i-dd zi Ur n Ikaldaniyyen uca teggid as Ibrahim. \x ◘ \xo 9:7 \xt Amz. 11:31, 32; 12:1\x*   
\m
\v 8 Cek tufid uř nnes dayes řaman zzat i wudem nnec u teggid akides Řɛahd belli Cek ad tewced i zzariɛet nnes tammurt n ayt n Kenɛan, n Iḥittiyyen, n Imuriyyen, n Ifariziyyen, n Iyabusiyyen u n Ijirjasiyyen, uca teggid ɛlaḥsab awařen nnec, minzi Cek d amsegged i teǧid. \x ◘ \xo 9:8 \xt Amz. 12:7; 13:15; 15:6, 18; 17:8; 26:4\x*   
\m
\v 9 Cek teẓriḍ tamara n řejdud nneɣ di Miṣra u tesřid iɣuyyan nsen zi ɣar Řebḥar n Telga. \x ◘ \xo 9:9 \xt Uf. 3:7; 14:10\x*   
\m
\v 10 Cek teggid řeɛřamat d lmuɛjizat ɣar firɛun u ɣar marra imsexxaren nnes u jar řgens n temmurt, minzi Cek tessned, aqa nitni ggin ḍidd nsen s tuffet uca Cek teggid i yixef nnec ijj n Isem, am \add teǧa\add* ass-a. \x ◘ \xo 9:10 \xt Uf. 7; 8; 9; 10; 11; 12; 14\x*   
\m
\v 11 Cek tebḍid řebḥar zzat i wudem nsen ařami nitni ɛdun x \add temmurt\add* yuẓɣen di řwesṭ n řebḥar, uca inni xasen ittaẓẓřen tenḍared ten di řaǧaɣ am yijj n weẓru deg waman ijehden. \x ◘ \xo 9:11 \xt Uf. 14:22-31\x*   
\m
\v 12 Zeg ijj n uqellij n useynu tgewwded ten s wass u s yijj n uqellij n tmessi s ǧiřet, ḥima ad asen tewced tafawt x webrid i x i ɣa uyuren. \x ◘ \xo 9:12 \xt Uf. 13:21; 14:19; 40:38; Izhd. 105:39\x*   
\m
\v 13 Cek tehwid-dd x wedrar n Sina u tessiwřed akidsen zeg ujenna uca tewcid asen lfarayiḍ iseggden d izerfan i di iǧa řaman d tweṣṣa d řumurat iṣebḥen. \x ◘ \xo 9:13 \xt Uf. 19:20; 20:1-21\x*   
\m
\v 14 Tessecned asen ssebt nnec iqeddsen uca teggid xasen řumurat d tweṣṣa d Ccariɛa s tsexxart n Musa, amsexxar nnec.   
\m
\v 15 Cek tewcid asen aɣrum zeg ujenna i řaẓ nsen uca tessuffɣed asen-dd aman zi teṣḍart i ufadi nsen uca tennid asen ad adfen ɣar temmurt, tenni i tessgeɛɛded afus nnec \add ḥima ad tejjaǧed\add* ad ten tt-i-dd-tewced, ḥima ad tt ṭṭfen d řwart.” \x ◘ \xo 9:15 \xt Uf. 16:14; 17:6; Řxř. 20:9\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 16 “Aqa nitni ak-d řejdud nneɣ ggin s tuffet d tɣennant u war sřin ca ɣar řumurat nnec.   
\m
\v 17 Nitni ugin ad ɣares sřen, war fekkaren di lmuɛjizat nnec i ɣarsen teggid u nitni ɣennan u deg uɣewweɣ nsen ggin ijj d uzeǧif \add x yixef nsen\add* ḥima ad ɛeqben ɣar tesmuɣi nsen. \add Maca\add* Cek d ijj n Arebbi iɣeffaren, dayek řxaḍar d arreḥmet, ɣarek ttasiɛ n řxaḍar d tamexsiwt icewwaren s waṭṭas, u Cek war daysen tesmiḥed ca. \x ◘ \xo 9:17 \xt Uf. 34:7; Řxř. 14:4, 18; Izhd. 86:5\x*   
\m
\v 18 Ɛad, umi ggin nitni ijj n uɛejmi ifesyen i yixef nsen, nnan: ‘Wa d arebbi nnec i cek i dd-issuffɣen zi Miṣra’, uca ceqqfen aṭṭas, \f ◼ \fr 9:18 \ft \+fk aɛejmi\ft  - niɣ ‘amwa’, ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 9:18 \xt Uf. 32\x*  
\v 19 aqa Cek di arreḥmet nnec tameqqrant war ten tejjid ca di řexřa. Aqellij n useynu \add i iǧan\add* ḥima ad ten igewwed s wass, war xasen iggʷij ca, uřa d aqellij n tmessi \add i iǧan\add* ḥima ad asen iwc tafawt deg webrid i x i ɣa uyuren, war xasen iggʷij ca s ǧiřet. \x ◘ \xo 9:19 \xt Uf. 13:22; 40:38\x*   
\m
\v 20 Cek tewcid Arruḥ nnec aṣebḥan, ḥima ad ten isseřmed, u Cek war d asen tekkised ca ‘manna’ nnek zeg uqemmum nsen uca tewcid asen aman i ufadi nsen. \x ◘ \xo 9:20 \xt Řxř. 11:17; Yac. 5:12\x*   
\m
\v 21 Arebɛin n iseggʷusa cek tᵉtthellid daysen di řexřa. War ɣarsen ittxiṣṣa uřa d ca n řḥajjet, arruḍ nsen war yarci ca uca iḍaren nsen war uffen. \x ◘ \xo 9:21 \xt Aɛwd. 2:7; 8:4; 29:5\x*   
\m
\v 22 Cek tewcid asen marra tigeldiwin d řegnus uca tebḍid asen ten d tasɣart s ijj n weymir. Nitni ṭṭfen tammurt n Siḥun d řwart, aqa-tt d tammurt n ujeǧid n Ḥacbun, d temmurt n Ɛuj, ajeǧid n Bacan. \x ◘ \xo 9:22 \xt Řxř. 21:21, 33\x*   
\m
\v 23 Cek tarrid iḥenjiren nsen aṭṭas am yitran deg ujenna u tessidfed ten ɣar temmurt i x tuɣa tennid i řejdud nsen, ad ɣares dd-adfen ḥima ad tt ṭṭfen d řwart. \x ◘ \xo 9:23 \xt Amz. 22:17\x*   
\m
\v 24 Yudef ɣares warraw uca ṭṭfen tt d řwart u zzat i wudem nsen aqa teggid imezdaɣ n temmurt sadu afus nsen, uřa d ijeǧiden nsen d řegnus n temmurt, ḥima ad zzaysen ggen min i d asen ittɣiř mliḥ.   
\m
\v 25 Nitni ḥewwsen tineddam ifaryen d ict n temmurt isseɣmayen u nitni ṭṭfen ɛawed tudrin d řwart ccurent s marra řxar, anuten ittwaɣzen, imarjaɛen n uḍiř d řeɛraṣit n zzitun d tcejjura n fruta s ufeyyeḍ, uca nitni ccin, jjiwnen, dewřen ṣeḥḥen uca arrin-dd meẓri s tcuni nnec tameqqrant.   
\m
\v 26 \add Maca nitni\add* dewřen war ṭṭiɛen uca ɣewwɣen xak uca nḍaren Ccariɛa nnec u nɣin inabiyyen nnec inni tuɣa icehhden jar asen maḥend ad ten dd-arren ɣarek. Aqa ceqqfen dayek s yijj n uceqqef imɣar. \x ◘ \xo 9:26 \xt 1 Ij. 18:4; 19:10; 2 Im. 24:20, 21\x*   
\m
\v 27 S uya tarrid ten deg ufus n iɣrimen nsen inni i ten iḥṣaren, \add maca\add* mařa řaɣan-dd xak di řweqt n řeḥṣaret nsen, \add xenni\add* tesřid ɣarsen zeg ujenna uca di arreḥmet nnec tameqqrant tewcid asen imsenjamen nni i ten ifekken zeg ufus n iɣrimen nsen. \x ◘ \xo 9:27 \xt Řqḍ. 2:14-23\x*   
\m
\v 28 Mařa ufin řhudnet, ggin ɛawed řɣar zzat i wudem nnec uca teggid ten deg ufus n řɛedyan nsen uca nitni seǧḍen xasen. Umi tuben, řaɣan-dd xak, aqa tesřid asen zeg ujenna u \add ammu i\add* tfekked i-ten s arreḥmet nnec aṭṭas n twařawin.   
\m
\v 29 Cek tcehded ḍidd nsen ḥima ad dd-ɛeqben ɣar Ccariɛa nnec, maca nitni ggin s tuffet u war sřin ca ɣar tweṣṣa nnec. Aqa xḍan zi jjihet n lfarayiḍ nnec, umi bnadem wenni i zzaysen i ɣa yegg ad zzaysent iddar, uca nitni arrin-dd ɣarsen aɛrur, tuɣa ssqesḥen iri nsen, war ɣarek dd-sřin. \x ◘ \xo 9:29 \xt Lawi 18:5; Ḥiz. 20:11; Rum. 10:5; Gal. 3:12\x*   
\m
\v 30 Aṭṭas n iseggʷusa tḥemmřed akidsen, tcehded ḍidd i nsen s Arruḥ nnec, s tsexxart n inabiyyen, maca nitni war sřin. \add S uyenni\add* tewcid ten deg ufus n řegnus n temmura. \x ◘ \xo 9:30 \xt 2 Ij. 17:13; 2 Im. 36:15\x*   
\m
\v 31 \add Maca\add* di arreḥmet nnec tameqqrant war ten taredǧed ca u war daysen tesmiḥed ca, maɣar cek d ijj n Arebbi d aḥnin d arḥim.   
\b  
\m
\v 32 “Xenni řexxu, AREBBI nneɣ, aqa Cek, Arebbi d ameqqran, izemmaren, issaggʷaden, wenni ittᵉṭṭfen di Řɛahd u di tmexsiwt icewwaren, war ḥesseb ca drus marra řeɣben i xaneɣ dd-ikkin, x ijeǧiden nneɣ, x řḥukkam nneɣ u x ikehhanen nneɣ u x inabiyyen nneɣ u x řejdud nneɣ u x marra řgens nneɣ zeg wussan n ijeǧiden n Accur ař ass-a.   
\m
\v 33 \add Tuɣa\add* Cek d amsegged di marra min xaneɣ ikkin, maɣar Cek teggid aneɣ s řaman, \add maca\add* neccin negga s řeqjaḥet. \x ◘ \xo 9:33 \xt Aɛwd. 32:4; Dan. 9:14\x*   
\m
\v 34 Ijeǧiden nneɣ, řḥukkam nneɣ, ikehhanen nneɣ d řejdud nneɣ war ḍeffaren Ccariɛa nnec uca war sřin ɣar řumurat nnec uřa ɣar cchadat nnec nni tcehded ḍidd i nsen.   
\m
\v 35 S tgeldit nsen u s řxar nsen aṭṭas i d asen tewcid u s temmurt tameqqrant isseɣmayen i d asen tewcid, war Cek sexxaren ca uca war tuben zi tmegga nsen tiɛeffanin.   
\m
\v 36 Xzar ass-a aqa neccin d imsemɣan u tammurt i tewcid i řejdud nneɣ maḥend ad zzayes necc řɣiǧet d řxar, xzar aqa neccin d imsemɣan i dayes \add neǧa\add*.   
\m
\v 37 Řɣiǧet tameqqrant nnes \add ad traḥ\add* ɣar ijeǧiden, inni i xaneɣ teggid di ssibbet n ddnub nneɣ, uca nitni ttṣeǧaḍen x arrayem nneɣ u x řmař nneɣ am mammec d asen ittɣiř mliḥ, u neccin aqa aneɣ di řeḥṣaret d tameqqrant.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 10
\s1 Řɛahd d tmarsiwt n ucemmeɛ  
\m
\v 1 “X qaɛ man aya ad negg ijj n řɛahd imten uca ad t nzemmem di tira uca řḥukkam nneɣ, Ilawiyyen nneɣ d ikehhanen nneɣ ad xas ggen acemmiɛ.”  
\v 2 Inni xas iggin acemmiɛ d ina:  
\m \bd Naḥamya, wenni d lwali ameqqran, mmis n Ḥakalya,\bd* d Ṣidqiya,  
\v 3 Saraya, Ɛazarya, Irmiya,  
\v 4 Facḥur, Amarya, Malkiya,  
\v 5 Ḥattuc, Cabanya, Mallux,  
\v 6 Ḥarim, Marimut, Ɛubadya,  
\v 7 Daniyal, Jinnitun, Barux,  
\v 8 Macullam, Abiya, Miyamin,  
\v 9 Maɛazya, Biljay d Camɛiya. \bd Ina tuɣa aten d ikehhanen\bd*.   
\m
\v 10 Uca \bd Ilawiyyen\bd*: Yecuɛa, mmis n Azanya, d Binnay. Zeg ayt n Ḥinadad, Qadmiyil.  
\v 11 Uřa d aytmatsen: Cabanya, Hudiya, Qaliṭa, Qalaya, Ḥanan,  
\v 12 Mixa, Raḥub, Ḥacabya,  
\v 13 Zakkur, Carabya, Cabanya,  
\v 14 Hudiya, Bani d Baninu.   
\m
\v 15 \bd Izeǧifen n řgens\bd*: Farɛuc, Faḥat-Mu’ab, Ɛilam, Zattu, Bani,  
\v 16 Bunni, Ɛazjad, Bibay,  
\v 17 Aduniya, Biɣway, Ɛadin,  
\v 18 Aṭir, Ḥizqiya, Ɛazzur,  
\v 19 Hudiya, Ḥacum, Biṣay,  
\v 20 Ḥarif, Ɛanatut, Nibay,  
\v 21 Majfiɛac, Macullam, Ḥazir,  
\v 22 Macizabyil, Ṣaduq, Yadduɛ,  
\v 23 Falaṭya, Ḥanan, Ɛanaya,  
\v 24 Huciɛa, Ḥananya, Ḥacub,  
\v 25 Halluḥic, Filja, Cubiq,  
\v 26 Raḥum, Ḥacabna, Maɛasiya,  
\v 27 Axiya, Ḥanan, Ɛanan,  
\v 28 Mallux, Ḥarim d Baɛna.   
\b  
\m
\v 29 Inni iqqimen zi řgens, ikehhanen, Ilawiyyen, iɛessasen n tewwura, imedyazen, imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant d marra inni d iɛezzřen ixef nsen x řegnus n temmura ɣar Ccariɛa n AREBBI, timɣarin nsen, iḥenjiren nsen d yessitsen, kuř ijj wenni ɣar teǧa tussna d řefhamet, \f ◼ \fr 10:29 \ft \+fk imedyazen\ft  - niɣ ‘imeɣnujen’.\f*  
\v 30 nitni \add marra\add* řeṣqen ɣar aytmatsen, ayt n bu-ṣṣulṭa nsen, uca ccarcen di nneɛřet d tjaǧit maḥend ad ddaren ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa n AREBBI, tenni immewcen x ufus n Musa, amsexxar n AREBBI, uca \add mahend\add* ad ḥḍan marra řumurat n SIDI, Siditneɣ, uca ad ṭṭfen di lfarayiḍ nnes d tweṣṣa nnes.  
\v 31 \add Ɛawed negga xaneɣ\add* maḥend war nettic yessitneɣ i řegnus n temmurt u war nettiwi yessitsen i iḥenjiren nneɣ \add d tamɣart\add*. \x ◘ \xo 10:31 \xt Uf. 34:16; Aɛwd. 7:3\x*   
\m
\v 32 Uca mařa řegnus n temmurt usin-dd deg wass n ssebt, iwyen ṣṣeřɛet d ɛřam kuř imendi ḥima ad zzenzen aya, aqa neccin di ssebt niɣ deg ijj n wass iqeddsen nneɣni war xasen nettiwi walu. Uca \add ammu ɛawed negga xaneɣ\add*, aqa neccin ad nejj \add tammurt\add* deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa u war nkessi arriba zeg uřa d yijjen. \x ◘ \xo 10:32 \xt Uf. 20:10; 23:10; 34:21; Lawi 23:2; 25:2; Aɛwd. 5:1-15\x*   
\m
\v 33 Negga xaneɣ řumurat maḥend ad newc ict n ttuřut n ciqlu deg useggʷas i tsexxart n Taddart n AREBBI nneɣ,  
\v 34 i weɣrum n wescan u i tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* n řebda u i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ n řebda deg wussan n ssebt u deg wussan n uyur n jdid, i řeɛyudat ittwaggen, i tmesřayin iqeddsen u i tɣarṣa n ddenb maḥend ad \add zzaysent\add* ittwagg aṣřaḥ x Israil u x marra tasexxart n Taddart n AREBBI nneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 10:34 \xt Řxř. 28:29\x*   
\m
\v 35 Neccin, ikehhanen, Ilawiyyen d řgens, \add am nᵉttwasettef\add* ɛlaḥsab řaǧat n ibabaten nneɣ, ggin taqedduḥt i tewhibt n ukeccuḍ tenni tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad tᵉttwassidef ɣar Taddart n AREBBI nneɣ deg wussan ittwaggen, aseggʷas awarni i useggʷas, maḥend ad tᵉttwassecmeḍ x uɛalṭar n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, am mammec i tura di Ccariɛa. \f ◼ \fr 10:35 \ft \+fk ussan\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ikuden’.\f*   
\m
\v 36 Uca \add negga xaneɣ ɛawed\add* maḥend ad nawi tamenzut n temmurt nneɣ d tmenzut n řɣiǧet n marra ticejjura ɣar Taddart n SIDI, aseggʷas x umas, \x ◘ \xo 10:36 \xt Uf. 23:19; Lawi 19:23\x*  
\v 37 uřa d imenza n iḥenjiren nneɣ d řebhayem nneɣ am mammec i tura di Ccariɛa, uca ad nawi imenza n ifunasen nneɣ d wuǧi nneɣ di Taddart n AREBBI, ɣar ikehhanen nni ittsexxaren di Taddart n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 10:37 \xt Uf. 13:2; Řxř. 3:13; 8:17\x*   
\m
\v 38 Uca \add negga xaneɣ ɛawed\add* maḥend ad nettawi tamezwarut \add n min ittwaggen\add* zeg warecti nneɣ u zi tewhibin n usgeɛɛed nneɣ u zi fruta n marra ticejjura u zi binu n jdid d zzect ɣar ikehhanen deg ixxamen \add i řexzen\add* n Taddart n AREBBI nneɣ, uřa d řeɛcur n temmurt nneɣ ɣar Ilawiyyen. Uca Ilawiyyen \add simant nsen\add* ad ṭṭfen řeɛcur di marra tineddam mani tuɣa nxeddem neccin x temmurt, \x ◘ \xo 10:38 \xt Lawi 23:17; Řxř. 15:19; 18:12, 24, 25; Aɛwd. 18:4\x*  
\v 39 uca ad yiři ukehhan, ijj n mmis n Harun, ɣar Ilawiyyen xmi ɣa ṭṭfenIlawiyyen řeɛcur. Uca Ilawiyyen \add simant nsen\add* ad awyen ict n teɛcart n řeɛcur ɣar Taddart n AREBBI, ɣar ixxamen n taddart n txubay, \f ◼ \fr 10:39 \ft \+fk tixubay\ft  - niɣ ‘řeknuz’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 10:39 \xt Řxř. 18:26\x*  
\v 40 minzi ayt n Israil d ayt n Lawi ad awyen tawhibt n usgeɛɛed n řḥebb \add n yirden\add*, řa n binu n jdid uřa n zzect deg ixxamen \add i řexzen\add*. Maɣar řeqcuɛ n Zzawect Iqeddsen aqa aten din, uřa d ikehhanen nni ittsexxaren d iɛessasen n tewwura d imedyazen. Ittxeṣṣa aneɣ war nsemmeḥ ca di Taddart n AREBBI nneɣ.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 11
\s1 Imezdaɣ n jdid n Urcalim u n tneddam iqqimen  
\m
\v 1 Řḥukkam n řgens qqimen zeddɣen di Urcalim, \add umi\add* řgens iqqimen igga taqedduḥt maḥend ijj zi ɛecra ad izdeɣ di Urcalim, tandint iqeddsen, u tesɛa di tneddam nneɣni.  
\v 2 Ibarek řgens marra iryazen nni iqeddmen ixef nsen s řxaḍar maḥend ad zedɣen di Urcalim.   
\m
\v 3 \bd Ina d izeǧifen n lɛamala, inni tuɣa izeddɣen di Urcalim.\bd* Tuɣa zeddɣen \add ayt n\add* Israil, ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen d imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant d ayt n isemɣan n Suliman di tneddam n Yahuda, kuř ijj deg wagřa nnes, di tneddam nsen.  
\v 4 Di Urcalim tuɣa zeddɣen ca zeg ayt n Yahuda u zeg ayt n Binyamin.  
\m \bd Zeg ayt n Yahuda\bd*: Ɛataya, mmis n Ɛuzziya, mmis n Zakariyya, mmis n Amarya, mmis n Cafaṭya, mmis n Mahalal-Il, zeg ayt n Fariṣ,  
\v 5 uřa d Maɛasiya, mmis n Barux, mmis n Kulḥuza, mmis n Ḥazaya, mmis n Ɛadaya, mmis n Yuyarib, mmis n Zakariyya, mmis n Uciluni. \f ◼ \fr 11:5 \ft \+fk Aciluni\ft  - ijj n weryaz zi tendint n Cilu.\f*  
\v 6 Marra ayt n Fariṣ inni izeddɣen di Urcalim, \add aqa aten\add* arebɛa-mya u-tmenya u-settin n iɛeskariyyen.   
\m
\v 7 Ina d \bd ayt n Binyamin\bd*: Sallu, mmis n Macullam, mmis n Yuɛid, mmis n Fadaya, mmis n Qulaya, mmis n Maɛasiya, mmis n Itiyil, mmis n Icaɛya  
\v 8 u awarni as Jabbay, Sallay: tesɛa-mya u-tmenya u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*.   
\m
\v 9 Tuɣa Yuwil, mmis n Zikri, d aweqqaf xasen u Yahuda, mmis n Hasnuwa tuɣa d \add ameḥḍay\add* wiss tnayen x tendint.   
\b  
\m
\v 10 \bd Zeg ikehhanen\bd*: Yadaɛya, mmis n Yuyarib, Yakin,  
\v 11 Saraya, mmis n Ḥilqiya, mmis n Macullam, mmis n Ṣaduq, mmis n Marayut, mmis n Axiṭub, ameḥḍay n Taddart n AREBBI,  
\v 12 uca aytmatsen, inni ixeddmen di Taddart, \add marra idsen\add* temn-mya u-tnayen u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*. \add Xenni\add* Ɛadaya, mmis n Yaruḥam, mmis n Falalya, mmis n Amṣi, mmis n Zakariyya, mmis n Facḥur, mmis n Malkiya,  
\v 13 d aytmas, izeǧifen n řaǧat, marra idsen mitayen u-tnayen u-rebɛin \add n yeryazen\add*. \add Xenni\add* Amcisay, mmis n Ɛazaryil, mmis n Axzay, mmis n Maclimut, mmis n Immir  
\v 14 d aytmatsen, ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen, marra idsen mya u-tmenya u-ɛicrin \add n yeryazen\add*. Tuɣa Zabdiyil, mmis n Hajdulim, d aweqqaf xasen.   
\m
\v 15 \bd Zeg Ilawiyyen\bd*: Camɛiya, mmis n Ḥaccub, mmis n Ɛazriqam, mmis n Ḥacabya, mmis n Bunni.  
\v 16 Cabbatay d Yuzabad, aqa nitni bedden ak-d řxedmet di barra n Taddart n AREBBI. Nitni zeg izeǧifen n Ilawiyyen.  
\v 17 Uca \add xenni\add* Mattanya, mmis n Mixa, mmis n Zabdi, mmis n Asaf, azeǧif i yarezmen taẓaǧit s ict n tẓaǧit n uqadi, d Baqbuqya wenni tuɣa d wiss tnayen zeg aytmas, u Ɛabda, mmis n Cammuɛa, mmis n Jalal, mmis n Yadatun.  
\v 18 Marra Ilawiyyen i iǧan di tendint iqeddsen, \add marra idsen\add*: mitayen u-arebɛa u-tmanin.   
\m
\v 19 \bd Iɛessasen n tewwura\bd*: Ɛaqqub, Ṭalmun ak-d aytmatsen, inni iṭṭfen aḥeṭṭu di tewwura \add n tendint\add*, \add marra idsen\add* mya u-tnayen u-sebɛin.   
\m
\v 20 Inni iqqimen n ayt Israil, ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen, zedɣen di tneddam n Yahuda, kuř ijj di tesɣart nnes.   
\m
\v 21 \bd Imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant\bd* zedɣen di Ɛufil. Tuɣa Ṣiḥa d Jicfa x imsexxaren n Zzawect Tameqqrant.   
\m
\v 22 Tuɣa Ɛuzzi, mmis n Bani, mmis n Ḥacabya, mmis n Mattanya, mmis n Mixa d aweqqaf n Ilawiyyen di Urcalim.  
\m Zeg ayt n Asaf tuɣa imedyazen x řxedmet di Taddart n AREBBI. \f ◼ \fr 11:22 \ft \+fk imedyazen\ft  - niɣ ‘imeɣnujen’.\f*  
\v 23 Maɣar tuɣa din xasen ict n tewṣeyyet n ujeǧid u x imedyazen \add tuɣa din\add* ijj n weqqan, kuř ass ict n tewṣeyyet \add i ittřiqen\add* i wass nni. \f ◼ \fr 11:23 \ft \+fk ict n tewṣeyyet\ft  - s Tiɛbranit ‘ijj n wawař’.\f*   
\m
\v 24 Tuɣa Faṭaḥya, mmis n Macizabyil, zeg ayt n Zaraḥ, mmis n Yahuda, d afus afusi n ujeǧid di marra min iřeqqfen řgens.   
\b  
\m
\v 25 \bd Di dcurat\bd* ɣar iyyaren nsen tuɣa din ca \bd zeg ayt n Yahuda\bd* inni tuɣa izeddɣen di Qaryat-Arebɛa d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen u di Dibbun d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen u di Yaqabṣiyil d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen  
\v 26 u di Yecuɛa u di Mulada u di Bayt-Falaṭ  
\v 27 u di Haṣar-Cuɛal u di Bi’r-Sebɛa d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen,  
\v 28 u di Ṣiqlaɣ u di Makuna d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen  
\v 29 u di Ɛayn-Rimmun u di Ṣarɛa u di Yarmut,  
\v 30 Zanuḥa, Adullam d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen, Laxic d iyyaren nnes, Ɛaziqqa d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen. Nitni wtin iqiḍan nsen zi Bi’r-Sebɛa ař taɣzurt n Hinnum.   
\m
\v 31 Tuɣa \bd ayt n Binyamin\bd* zeddɣen zi Jabaɛ di Mixmas d Ɛaya d Bayt-Il d tneddam i ɣarsen dd-iqqnen,  
\v 32 Ɛanatut, Nub, Ɛananya,  
\v 33 Haṣur, Rama, Jittayim,  
\v 34 Ḥadid, Ṣabuɛim, Naballaṭ,  
\v 35 Lud d Unu \add d\add* Teɣzurt n Teɣzurt n Iḥrayfiyyen.   
\m
\v 36 \bd Zeg Ilawiyyen\bd* \add zedɣen din\add* terbiḥin zi Yahuda ɣar Binyamin.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 12
\s1 Lista n ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen  
\m
\v 1 Ina d ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen inni dd-igeɛɛden ak-d Zarubabbil, mmis n Caɛaltiyil, d Yahucaɛ: Saraya, Irmiya, Ɛizra,  
\v 2 Amarya, Mallux, Ḥaṭṭuc,  
\v 3 Cakanya, Raḥum, Marimut,  
\v 4 Ɛiddu, Jinnituy, Abiya,  
\v 5 Miyamin, Maɛadya, Bilja,  
\v 6 Camɛiya, Yuyarib, Yadaɛya,  
\v 7 Sallu, Ɛamuq, Ḥilqiya d Yadɛaya. Ina d izeǧifen n ikehhanen d aytmas deg wussan n Yahucaɛ.   
\m
\v 8 Uca Ilawiyyen \add d ina\add*: Yecuɛa, Binnuy, Qadmiyil, Carabya, Yahuda d Mattanya, \add wenni\add* iǧan x izřan n uqadi, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d aytmas.  
\v 9 Baqbuqya d Ɛunni, aytmatsen, tuɣa ḥeṭṭan arendad nsen.   
\b  
\m
\v 10 Yecuɛa ijja-dd Yuyaqim, u Yuyaqim ijja-dd Ilyacib, u Ilyacib ijja-dd Yuyadaɛ,  
\v 11 u Yuyadaɛ ijja-dd Yunatan, u Yunatan ijja-dd Yadduɛ.   
\b  
\m
\v 12 Deg wussan n Yuyaqim tuɣa d izeǧifen-a n \add řaǧat n\add* ibabaten d ikehhanen:  
\m i \add řaǧat n\add* Saraya: Maraya,  
\m i \add řaǧat n\add* Irmiya: Ḥananya,   
\m
\v 13 i \add řaǧat n\add* Ɛizra: Macullam,  
\m i \add řaǧat n\add* Amarya: Yuḥanan,   
\m
\v 14 i \add řaǧat n\add* Maliku: Yunatan,  
\m i \add řaǧat n\add* Cabinya: Yusuf,   
\m
\v 15 i \add řaǧat n\add* Ḥarim: Ɛadna,  
\m i \add řaǧat n\add* Marayut: Ḥilqay,   
\m
\v 16 i \add řaǧat n\add* Ɛiddu: Zakariyya,  
\m i \add řaǧat n\add* Jinnitun: Macullam,   
\m
\v 17 i \add řaǧat n\add* Abiya: Zikri,  
\m i \add řaǧat n\add* Minyamin d Muɛadya: Filṭay,   
\m
\v 18 i \add řaǧat n\add* Bilja: Cammuɛa,  
\m i \add řaǧat n\add* Camɛiya: Yunatan,   
\m
\v 19 i \add řaǧat n\add* Yuyarib: Mattanay,  
\m i \add řaǧat n\add* Ɛuzzi: Yadaɛya,   
\m
\v 20 i \add řaǧat n\add* Sallay: Qallay,  
\m i \add řaǧat n\add* Ɛamuq: Ɛabir,   
\m
\v 21 i \add řaǧat n\add* Ḥilqiya: Ḥacabya  
\m u i \add řaǧat n\add* Yadaɛya: Natanayil.   
\m
\v 22 Deg wussan n Ilyasib, Yuyadaɛ, Yuḥanan d Yadduɛ, ttwazemmemen izeǧifen x ibabaten \add n řaǧat\add* n Ilawiyyen uřa d ikehhanen ař tagelda n Dariyus, Afarsi.  
\v 23 Ttwazemmemen ayt n Lawi, izeǧifen x ibabaten \add n řaǧat\add*, deg wedlis n imezruyen ař ussan n Yuḥanan, mmis n Ilyacib. \x ◘ \xo 12:23 \xt 1 Im. 9:10-34\x*   
\m
\v 24 Izeǧifen n Ilawiyyen tuɣa Ḥacabya, Carabya d Yecuɛa, mmis n Qadmiyil, u aytmatsen \add bedden\add* ajemmaḍin nsen ḥima ad ssemɣaren u ad qadan, am mammec tuɣa teǧa tewṣeyyet n Dawud, aryaz n AREBBI. Ijj tuɣa iḥeṭṭan arendad n wenneɣni i tuɣa iḥeṭṭan.   
\m
\v 25 Tuɣa Mattanya, Baqbuqya, Ɛubadya, Macullam, Ṭalmum d Ɛaqqub iɛessasen n tewwart inni iɛessen x ixxamen n řexzen n tewwura \add n tendint\add*.  
\v 26 Ina tuɣa aten deg wussan n Yuyaqim, mmis n Yahucaɛ mmis n Yuṣadaq, uřa deg wussan n Naḥamya, lwali, u n ukehhan Ɛizra, amseřmed n idlisen.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Adeccen n řḥiḍ n Urcalim  
\m
\v 27 Ɣar udeccen n řḥiḍ n Urcalim arzun nitni x Ilawiyyen di marra imucan nsen maḥend ad ten awyen ɣar Urcalim ḥima nitni ad ssqefřen adeccen, ad ggen řefraḥet s uqadi u s yezřan, s teǧunin n wuzzař, s lharpat d řgambriyat.  
\v 28 Nitni ssmunen x ayt n imedyazen zeg udewwar n Urcalim u zi dcurat n Unaṭufati,  
\v 29 u zi Bayt-Jiljal uřa zeg iyyaren n Jiba d Ɛazmawet, minzi imedyazen bnan i yixef nsen dcurat i dd-innḍen i Urcalim.  
\v 30 Ssizedgen ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen ixef nsen uca awarni i uya ssizedgen nitni uřa d řgens d tewwura d řḥiḍ.   
\m
\v 31 \add Xenni\add* ggiɣ řḥukkam n Yahuda ad nyen x řḥiḍ u ssbeddeɣ tnayen n terbiɛin n uɣennej i uqadi. Tuyur ict \add n terbiɛt\add* ɣar yefus sennej x řḥiḍ ɣar Tewwart n Řeɣbar.  
\v 32 Yareddef i-tt Hucaɛya s yijj n wezyen n řḥukkam n Yahuda,  
\v 33 Ɛazarya, Ɛizra, Macullam,  
\v 34 Yahuda, Binyamin, Camɛiya d Irmiya,  
\v 35 u zeg ayt n ikehhanen inni ɣarsen řebwaq: Zakariyya, mmis n Yunatan, mmis n Camɛiya, mmis n Mattanya, mmis n Mixa-Yah, mmis n Zakkur, mmis n Asaf,  
\v 36 d aytmas Camɛiya d Ɛazaryil, Milalay, Jilalay, Maɛay, Natanayil d Yahuda, Ḥanani ak-dduzan n řmusiqa n Dawud, aryaz n AREBBI, uca zzat i wudem nsen tuɣa iggur Ɛizra, amseřmed n idlisen.  
\v 37 Ɣar Tewwart n Tařa uca \add xenni nican\add* qibač nsen nyen ddrujjat n tendint n Dawud mani dd-igeɛɛed řḥiḍ, ttekken x taddart n Dawud ař Tawwart n Waman, ɣar ccarq.   
\m
\v 38 Tarbiḥt n uqadi wiss tnayen tuyur ɣar jjihet nneɣnit uca necc areddfeɣ tt ak-d wezyen \add nneɣni\add* n řgens, \add nekka\add* x řḥiḍ ɣar uɣezdis n Lburj n Tefqunt ař řḥiḍ amiriw,  
\v 39 uca xenni \add nekka\add* x Tewwart n Ifrayim u x Tewwart Taqdimt u x Tewwart n Iseřman d Lburj n Ḥananiyil d Lburj n Mya ař Tawwart n Wuǧi uca nitni qqimen bedden ɣar Tewwart n Řeḥbes.   
\m
\v 40 \add Xenni\add* beddent tnayen n terbiḥin n uqadi di Taddart n AREBBI, uřa d necc ak-d wezyen n imḍebbaren akidi.  
\v 41 \add Uřa\add* d ikehhanen Alyaqim, Maɛasiya, Minyamin, Mixa-Yah, Ilyuɛinay, Zakariyya, Ḥananya, inni ɣarsen řebwaq,  
\v 42 uca \add xenni\add* Maɛasiya d Camɛiya d Aliɛazar d Ɛuzzi d Yuḥanan d Malkiya d Ɛilam d Ɛazar. Imedyazen ggin ad ttwasřen u tuɣa Yizraḥa d aweqqaf.   
\m
\v 43 Deg wass nni wehhben nitni aṭṭas n tɣarṣa d timeqqranin. Marra farḥen, maɣar AREBBI igga asen ict n řefraḥet d tameqqrant. Farḥen uřa d timɣarin d iḥenjiren imeẓyanen ařami řefraḥet \add n řɛid\add* n Urcalim tuɣa ttesřan as zi řaggʷaj.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Taynit di ṭṭweɛ n tewhibin ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa n Musa  
\m
\v 44 Deg wussan nni ggin iryazen ad iřin x ixxamen \add i iǧan\add* i txubay, i tewhibin n usgeɛɛed, i usuffuɣ tamezwarut \add n ṣṣabet\add* u i řeɛcur, ḥima ad daysent yarwen tiseqqar i dd-ikkaren i ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen zeg iyyaren n tneddam ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa, maɣar farḥen \add ayt n\add* Yahuda zeg ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen nni i din ibedden \f ◼ \fr 12:44 \ft \+fk tixubay\ft  - niɣ ‘řeknuz’.\f*  
\v 45 u ḥḍan x tsexxart n AREBBI nsen u x tsexxart n usizdeg, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d imedyazen d iɛessasen n tewwura, ɛlaḥsab tawṣeyyet n Dawud d mmis Suliman. \x ◘ \xo 12:45 \xt 1 Im. 25\x*  
\v 46 Maɣar zic, deg wussan n Dawud d Adaf, \add tuɣa\add* din ijj n izeǧifen n imedyazen i izřan n uṣebbeḥ uřa i uqadi i AREBBI.  
\v 47 \add S uya\add* iwca marra Israil di marra ussan n Zarubbabil u deg wussan n Naḥamya tiseqqar n imedyazen d iɛessasen n tewwura, kuř tasɣart n ijj n wass deg wass nnes, uca ssqeddsen tt i Ilawiyyen uca Ilawiyyen ssqeddsen tt i warraw n Harun.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 13
\s1 Acḍar n Naḥamya di ṭṭweɛ n Ccariɛa  
\m
\v 1 Deg wass nni ɣrin deg imezzuɣen n řgens zeg wedlis n Musa uca ittwaf aqa tura dayes belli ijj n Uɛammuni d ijj n Umu’abiy ɛemmarṣ war zemmaren ad adfen ɣar wegraw \add n řgens\add* n AREBBI i řebda, \x ◘ \xo 13:1 \xt Aɛwd. 23:2, 4, 5\x*  
\v 2 maɣar nitni war ffiɣen ɣar ayt n Israil s weɣrum d waman, \add maca\add* cran Bilɛam ḍidd nsen maḥend ad ten inɛeř uca \add xenni\add* yarra AREBBI nneɣ nneɛřet d lbaraka.\x ◘ \xo 13:2 \xt Řxř. 22:5; Yac. 24:9\x*  
\v 3 Umi sřin Ccariɛa-aya, imsar, aqa bḍan x Israil marra inni ixeǧḍen zi taṣiřet.   
\m
\v 4 Qbeř issewjed Ilyacib, akehhan, wenni tuɣa x ixxamen \add i řexzen\add* n Taddart n AREBBI nneɣ, d wenni i itteɛnan i Ṭubiya,  
\v 5 ijj n wexxam d ameqqran i \add Tubiya\add* mani tuɣa \add xemmřen\add* qbeř tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*, jjawi d řeqcuɛ, řeɛcur n řḥebb \add n yirden\add*, d binu n jdid d zzect nni ttwaggen i Ilawiyyen, i imedyazen u i iɛessasen n tewwura, uřa d tɣarṣt n usgeɛɛed n ikehhanen.   
\m
\v 6 Di marra man aya war d ayi tuɣi ca di Urcalim, maɣar deg useggʷas wiss tnayen u-třatin n Artaḥcasta, ajeǧid n Babil, tuɣa ɛeqbeɣ ɣar ujeǧid. Awarni \add ijj n řmijař n\add* wussan ttareɣ zeg ujeǧid ttesriḥ \add maḥend ad dd-ɛeqbeɣ\add*.  
\v 7 \add Umi\add* iwḍeɣ ɣar Urcalim, iban-dd ayi řɣar nni igga Ilyacib di ṭṭweɛ n Ṭubiya umi d as issewjed ijj n wexxam di řemraḥat n Taddart n AREBBI.  
\v 8 Tuɣa aya d ict n tmesřact d taɛeffant aṭṭas di tiṭṭawin inu uca nḍareɣ marra řeqcuɛ n Ṭubiya zeg wexxam ɣar barra.  
\v 9 Nniɣ aqa ittxeṣṣa asen ad ssizedgen ixxamen. \add Awarni as\add* arriɣ daysen řeqcuɛ n Taddart n AREBBI, uřa d tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* d jjawi.   
\m
\v 10 Ttwassargbeɣ \add ɛawed\add*, aqa tiseqqar \add i dd-ittasen\add* i Ilawiyyen war d asen mmewcent ařami Ilawiyyen d imedyazen nni iggin řxedmet, arewřen, kuř ijj ɣar yeyyar nnes.  
\v 11 Mmcubbceɣ ak-d imḍebbaren, nniɣ: “Mayemmi tᵉttwasmeḥ Taddart n AREBBI?” U necc ssmuneɣ ten uca arreɣ ten-i-dd deg wemcan nsen.  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* yiwi-dd marra Yahuda řeɛcur n řḥebb \add n yirden\add* řa n binu n jdid uřa n zzect deg ixxamen n txubay.  
\v 13 Ggiɣ imeqqranen x ixxamen n txubay: akehhan Calamya d umarir Ṣaduq d Fadaya zeg Ilawiyyen uca ggiɣ asen ɣar uɣezdis Ḥanan, mmis n Zakkur, mmis n Mattanya, maɣar tuɣa ttwaḥesben d imtiqqan. Nitni xasen maḥend ad bḍan aya i aytmatsen.   
\m
\v 14 Idar ayi i man aya, \add a\add* AREBBI inu, u war tmeḥḥid tamexsiwt inu icewwaren nni ssecneɣ i Taddart n AREBBI inu u i tsexxart i dayes \add iǧan\add*.   
\b  
\m
\v 15 Deg wussan nni ẓriɣ aqa din di Yahuda inni ittcuqan di tsirt deg \add wass n\add* ssebt uřa d inni dd-iwyen icuwwafen n imendi, arbun ten x yeɣyař, uřa d binu, aḍiř, tazart d ɛřam kuř řeḥmuř nni iwyen deg wass n ssebt di Urcalim. Necc ɛeřmeɣ ten deg wass \add nni\add* umi tuɣa zznuzan macca deg wass n ssebt.  
\v 16 Tuɣa ayt n Ṣur zeddɣen dinni, iwyen-dd iseřman d marra sseřɛet, zznuzan aya di ssebt i ayt n Yahuda u di Urcalim.  
\v 17 Ɛeyyareɣ tarwa n taṣiřet n Yahuda, nniɣ asen: “Man tuɛeffna i tᵉtteggem i zi tessɛiǧtem ass n ssebt! \x ◘ \xo 13:17 \xt Uf. 20:8; Lawi 19:30\x*  
\v 18 Ma war ggin řejdud nwem amenni uca \add xenni\add* ma war dd-issiweḍ AREBBI nneɣ marra řɣar-a xaneɣ u x tendint-a? U kenniw tarennim \add ɛad\add* di řḥaduq \add n weɣḍab nnes\add* x Israil umi tessɛiǧtem ssebt.”   
\m
\v 19 Uca imsar xmi dd ɣa tewḍa taǧest di tewwura n Urcalim, qbeř ma ad dd-yaweḍ ssebt, aqa nniɣ ad ttwabellɛent tewwura uca arniɣ nniɣ ad tent arzmen awarni i ssebt waha. Uca ssbeddeɣ imsexxaren inu ɣar tewwura, maḥend war ssidifen uřa d ijj n řeḥmeř deg wass n ssebt.  
\v 20 Uca ammu issensen isebbaben d imzenzan n ɛřam kuř sseřɛet \add ɛad\add* ict niɣ tnayen n twařawin barra zzat i \add řeḥyuḍ n\add* Urcalim.  
\v 21 Uca cehdeɣ xasen, nniɣ asen: “Mayemmi tᵉttnusam kenniw x uɣezdis n řḥiḍ? Mařa kenniw teggim t twařa nneɣnit, ad xawem wteɣ afus.” Ssenni war dd-usin ɛad di ssebt.   
\m
\v 22 Nniɣ \add ɛawed\add* i Ilawiyyen ad ssizdegen ixef nsen, ad bedden d iɛessasen ɣar tewwura \add n tendint\add*, maḥend ad qeddsen ass n ssebt.  
\b  
\m Uřa i uya idar ayi, AREBBI inu,  
\m u ḥinn xafi  
\m ɛlaḥsab řemɣaret n tmexsiwt nnec icewwaren.   
\b  
\m
\v 23 Deg wussan nni ẓriɣ ɛawed Udayen nni iwyen timɣarin n Acdud d Ɛammun d Mu’ab uca ssezdɣen tent ɣarsen.  
\v 24 Azyen n iḥenjiren nsen ssawařen s iřes n Acdud, war zemmaren ad ssiwřen iřes n Tyahudect, maca kuř ijj \add tuɣa issawař\add* ɛlaḥsab iřes n kuř řgens. \f ◼ \fr 13:24 \ft \+fk iřes\ft  - niɣ ‘tutlayt’.\f*  
\v 25 Ɛeyyareɣ ten u neɛřeɣ ten u wtiɣ \add ca n\add* yeryazen zzaysen, qeřɛeɣ acuwwaf nsen u jjiɣ ten ad jjaǧen ɣar AREBBI: “Ɣarwem ad tewcem tiḥenjirin nwem i iḥenjiren nsen u ɣarwem ad tawyem tiḥenjirin nsen i iḥenjiren nwem niɣ i ixef nwem \add d tamɣart\add*!”  
\v 26 Ma war ixḍi Suliman, ajeǧid n Israil, di tmesřact-a? D man aya tuɣa umi war din iǧi d ajeǧid am netta jar waṭṭas n řegnus uca tuɣa ittexs i-t AREBBI u AREBBI igga i-t d ajeǧid x marra Israil? \add Waxxa amenni\add* ɣarrent t temɣarin tibarraniyyin maḥend ad ixḍa uřa d netta. \x ◘ \xo 13:26 \xt 1 Ij. 11:1-4; 1 Ij. 3:13; 2 Im. 1:12\x*  
\v 27 Ma xenni ad ɣarwem nseř \add ɛad ktar\add* umi tᵉtteggem marra řɣar-a ameqqran u tɣeddarem AREBBI uca tiwyem timɣarin tibarraniyyin maḥend ad kidwem zeddɣent?   
\m
\v 28 Ijjen zeg iḥenjiren n Yuyadaɛ, mmis n Ilyacib, arrays n ikehhanen tuɣa d aḍeggʷař n Sanballaṭ zi Ḥurun. S uya uẓẓřeɣ xas zi ɣari   
\m
\v 29 Idar asen, a AREBBI inu, minzi nitni ssxemjen tukehhant, \add řxedmet n ikehhanen\add*, d řɛahd n tukehhant u n Ilawiyyen.   
\m
\v 30 U necc ssizedgeɣ ten zi marra min tuɣa d řɣib, uca areccḥeɣ aḥeṭṭu n ikehhanen u n Ilawiyyen, kuř ijj di tsexxart nnes.  
\v 31 \add Ammu i ggiɣ\add* uřa i tewhibt n ukeccuḍ, di řweqt nnes ittwaggen, u i tmenzut \add n ṣṣabet\add*. Idar ayi, \add a\add* AREBBI inu, i řxar.   